'''麻省理工學院'''（{{lang-en|Massachusetts Institute of Technology}}，[[首字母縮略字|縮寫]]為{{lang|en|'''MIT'''}}；按现代中國大陸规范可译为“-{zh-hans:马萨诸塞; zh-hant:麻薩諸塞}-理工学院”，但不常用）是位於[[美國|美國]][[麻薩諸塞州|麻薩諸塞州]][[剑桥_(马萨诸塞州)|劍橋市]]的[[私立|私立]][[研究型大學|研究型大學]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=MIT School of Engineering {{!}} » About|url=https://engineering.mit.edu/about/|accessdate=2019-10-09|work=Mit Engineering|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191119112809/https://engineering.mit.edu/about/|archive-date=2019-11-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成立於1861年。主校区沿[[查尔斯河|查尔斯河]]而建，當時目的是為了響應{{link-en|美國技術與工業發展史|Technological and industrial history of the United States|美國與日俱增的工業化需求}}<ref name="charter" />。学校採用了{{link-en|歐洲研究型大學發展史|History of European research universities|歐洲理工大學的模式}}辦學，早期著力於[[應用科學|應用科學]]與[[工程學|工程學]]的實驗教學<ref name="polytechnic" />。學校的研究人員在[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]及[[冷戰|冷戰]]期間，致力開發[[電腦|電腦]]、[[雷達|雷達]]及[[慣性導航系統|慣性導航系統]]技術<ref name="RadLab" />；戰後的防禦性科技研究使學校得以進一步發展，教職員人數及校園面積在{{link-en|占士·賴恩基利安|James Rhyne Killian|-{zh:占士; zh-cn:詹姆斯; zh-hk:占士; zh-tw:詹姆士}-·賴恩基利安}}的帶領下有所上升<ref name="report_1949" />。大學於1916年遷往現在位於[[查爾斯河|查爾斯河]]北岸的校址，沿岸伸延逾{{convert|1|mi|km|1}}，佔地{{convert|168|acre|ha}}<ref name="new_campus" />。

麻省理工学院擁有6間學術學院、32個學系部門，常獲納入全球最佳學府之列<ref name="bloomberg1">{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/harvard-mit-ranked-most-prestigious-universities-study-reports.html|title=Harvard, MIT Ranked Most Prestigious Universities, Study Reports|author=David Altaner|publisher=Bloomberg|date=09/03/2011|accessdate=09/12/2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115040232/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/harvard-mit-ranked-most-prestigious-universities-study-reports.html|archive-date=2015-01-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="encyclopedia1">{{cite web|title=Massachusetts Institute of Technology|url=http://www.encyclopedia.com/topic/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology.aspx#2|publisher=Encyclopedia.com|quote="It has long been recognized as an outstanding technological institute and its Sloan School of Management has notable programs in business, economics, and finance."|accessdate=09/12/2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920194555/http://www.encyclopedia.com/topic/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology.aspx#2|archive-date=2015-09-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="britannica1">{{cite web|title=Massachusetts Institute of Technology|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/368456/Massachusetts-Institute-of-Technology-MIT|publisher=Encyclopedia Britannica|accessdate=09/12/2015|quote="Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT), privately controlled coeducational institution of higher learning famous for its scientific and technological training and research."|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503071418/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/368456/Massachusetts-Institute-of-Technology-MIT|archive-date=2015-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。學校一直聞名於[[物理科學|物理科學]]與[[工程學|工程學]]的教研，但在近代亦大力發展諸如[[生命科學|生命科學]]、[[經濟學|經濟學]]、[[管理學|管理學]]、[[語言學|語言學]]等其他學術範疇。別名「工程師」的麻省理工體育校隊合計31支，涵蓋不同項目，學生因此可參與不同類型的跨校體育聯賽。

麻省理工學院在2021年[[QS世界大學排名|QS世界大學排名]]中位列全球第一。截至2020年10月，麻省理工学院的校友、教授及研究人員涵蓋[[各大學諾貝爾獎得主列表|97位諾貝爾獎得主]]、[[各大学菲尔兹奖得主列表|8名菲爾茲獎獲獎者]]、[[各大学图灵奖得主列表|26位图灵奖得主]]，以及52位[[國家科學獎章|國家科學獎章]]獲獎者、45位[[羅德獎學金|羅德學者]]、38名[[麥克阿瑟獎|麥克阿瑟獎]]得主<ref>{{Cite web|title=Notable Awards {{!}} MIT CSAIL|url=https://www.csail.mit.edu/about/notable-awards|accessdate=2019-10-09|work=www.csail.mit.edu|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191005192654/https://www.csail.mit.edu/about/notable-awards|archive-date=2019-10-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。該校同時具很強的[[企業家精神|創業文化]]，由其校友所創辦的公司利潤總值相當於[[各國國內生產總值列表_(國際匯率)|全球第十一大經濟體]]（截至2014年）。<ref name=IRAwardsHonors/><ref>{{cite web |title=Entrepreneurial Impact The Role of MIT |url=http://www.kauffman.org/what-we-do/research/2009/08/entrepreneurial-impact-the-role-of-mit |work=http://www.kauffman.org/ |publisher=Ewing Marion Kauffman Foundation |date=2009-02-17 |accessdate=09/12/2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016005821/http://www.kauffman.org/what-we-do/research/2009/08/entrepreneurial-impact-the-role-of-mit |archive-date=2015-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==校史==
===創校使命===
{{multiple image
   | direction = vertical
   | width     = 200
   | align     = left
   | caption1    = 一張顯示了十九世紀的麻省理工機械工作室的{{link-en|實體鏡|Stereoscope|實體照卡片}}。
   | caption2    = 十九世紀麻省理工後灣區校園的羅傑斯大樓。
   | image1    = MIT Boston 19th c byEdward L Allen BPL 2351553844.jpg
   | image2    = Mass. Inst. Technology, by E. L. Allen.png
}}{{Quote box
 |align = left
 |quote = ......為一所工業科學院校，旨在結合文藝、農業、製造業、商業與科學，<br>並促進它們的進步、發展及應用。
 |source = ——{{small|麻省理工學院法團機構成立法案<br>《1861年法案第183章》}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/corporation/charter.html |title=MIT Charter |accessdate=09/12/2015 |date= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070222210537/http://web.mit.edu/corporation/charter.html |archive-date=2007-02-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 |fontsize = big
 |salign = right
}}

1859年，一份有關在新填海土地[[後灣區|後灣區]]興建一所文理學院的建議書遭[[麻省議會|-{zh:麻省;zh-hk:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞州;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞州;}-議會]]否決<ref>{{cite web |last=Kneeland |first=Samuel |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/pdf/house260.pdf |format=PDF |title=Committee Report: Conservatory of Art and Science |publisher=Massachusetts House of Representatives, House No. 260 |date=1859 |access-date=2015-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612090711/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/pdf/house260.pdf |archive-date=2010-06-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=MIT Timeline|url=http://libraries.mit.edu/sites/mithistory/mit-timeline/|work=MIT History|publisher=MIT Institute Archives|accessdate=09/12/2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130219203038/http://libraries.mit.edu/sites/mithistory/mit-timeline/|archive-date=2013-02-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[威廉·巴頓·羅傑斯|威廉·巴頓·羅傑斯]]隨後草議成立麻省理工學院法團校董會，有關文件在1861年4月10日獲得{{link-en|約翰·維奇安德魯|John Albion Andrew|州長}}的簽名批核<ref name=charter>{{cite web|title=Acts and Resolves of the General Court Relating to the Massachusetts Institute of Technology|url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/pdf/1861%20Charter.pdf|work=MIT History|publisher=MIT Institute Archives|accessdate=09/12/2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701055022/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/pdf/1861%20Charter.pdf|archive-date=2015-07-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。這位-{zh:維珍尼亞;zh-hk: 維珍尼亞;zh-cn:弗吉尼亚;zh-tw: 維吉尼亞}-大學的教授希望建立一所專科學府，以配合國內一日千里的科技發展<ref>{{cite web|title=MIT Facts 2012: Origins and Leadership|url=http://web.mit.edu/facts/origins.html|work=MIT Facts 2015|publisher=MIT|accessdate=09/12/2015|date=2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150831081249/http://web.mit.edu/facts/origins.html|archive-date=2015-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Rogers |first=William |publisher=The Committee of Associated Institutions of Science and Arts |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/pdf/objects-plan.pdf |format=PDF |title=Objects and Plan of an Institute of Technology: including a Society of Arts, a Museum of Arts, and a School of Industrial Science; proposed to be established in Boston |year=1861 |accessdate=09/12/2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612092224/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/pdf/objects-plan.pdf |archive-date=2010-06-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。純[[職業教育|專業學院]]不是他想要的類型，他認為[[博雅教育|博雅教育]]為不可或缺的元素之一。他在草議中寫道<ref>{{cite web |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/timeline/letter1846.html |title=Letter from William Barton Rogers to His Brother Henry |date=1846-03-13 |accessdate=09/12/2015 |publisher=Institute Archives, MIT |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105859/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/timeline/letter1846.html |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>：「以我之見，理工學校唯一且真正的價值在於教學。這不是指那些可在工作坊中學到的瑣碎細節或文藝批判，而是那些對自然萬物提供合理解釋的基礎科學原則。」

羅傑斯採納了德國研究型大學的辦學模式，提倡教研並重。教職員除了進行研究外，他們還會向學生提供講堂及實驗室教學<ref name=polytechnic/><ref>{{cite book|editor1-last=Geiger |editor1-first=Roger L. |last=Angulo |first=A.J. |chapter=The Initial Reception of MIT, 1860s–1880s |title=Perspectives on the History of Higher Education |pages=1–28}}</ref>。

===早期發展===
[[File:МИТ_кампус_1905.jpg|thumb]]
就在有關草議獲批兩天後，[[美國內戰|美國內戰]]的[[桑特堡戰役|第一場戰役]]就展開了。為時數年的戰爭使學校的教研工作延誤。1865年，麻省理工正式在位於波士頓的校園內開班<ref>{{cite web |last=Andrews |first=Elizabeth |first2=Nora |last2=Murphy |first3=Tom |last3=Rosko |year=2000 |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/wbr-visionary/ |publisher=MIT Archives |title=William Barton Rogers: MIT's Visionary Founder |access-date=2015-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080512091317/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/wbr-visionary/ |archive-date=2008-05-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。這所新院校的使命乎合《[[土地撥贈法案|土地撥贈法案]]》的要求，故獲贈地作進一步發展<ref>{{cite book|last1=Stratton |first1=Julius Adams |last2=Mannix |first2=Loretta H. |title=Mind and Hand: The Birth of MIT |url=https://archive.org/details/mindhandbirthmit00stra |pages=[https://archive.org/details/mindhandbirthmit00stra/page/n271 251]–276 |chapter=The Land-Grant Act of 1862 |isbn=0-262-19524-0 |publisher=MIT Press |year=2005}}</ref>。1866年，由土地銷售帶來的利益使學校得以在後灣區發展<ref name="BostonTech1">{{cite book|title=When M.I.T. Was "Boston Tech", 1861–1916 |last=Prescott |first=Samuel C |year=1954 |publisher=MIT Press}}</ref>。

「波士頓理工」為麻省理工學院的非正式別稱<ref name="BostonTech1" />。大學採用{{link-en|歐洲研究型大學發展史|History of European research universities|歐洲理工大學的模式}}辦學，早期比較重視實驗教學<ref name=polytechnic>{{cite book|last=Angulo |first=A.J. |title=William Barton Rogers and the Idea of MIT |year=2008 |url=https://archive.org/details/williambartonrog00angu |pages=[https://archive.org/details/williambartonrog00angu/page/155 155]–156|publisher=The Johns Hopkins University Press |isbn=0-8018-9033-0}}</ref>。雖一直受到財政問題困擾，但在{{link-en|弗朗西·斯亞瑪撒·沃克|Francis Amasa Walker}}的帶領下，學校還是在19世紀最後的20年裡不斷成長<ref name="Dunbar1">{{cite journal|last=Dunbar|first=Charles F.|title=The Career of Francis Amasa Walker|journal=Quarterly Journal of Economics|date=July 1897|volume=11|issue=4|pages=446–447|jstor=1880719|ref=harv}}</ref>，繼而開辦電子、化學、海洋及潔淨工程學<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/spotlight/tea-party/ |title=Explore campus, visit Boston, and find out if MIT fits you to a tea |date=2006-12-16 |accessdate=2006-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070211155218/http://web.mit.edu/spotlight/tea-party/ |archive-date=2007-02-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Munroe1923a">{{cite book|first=James P. |last=Munroe |publisher=Henry Holt & Company |year=1923 |title=A Life of Francis Amasa Walker |location=New York |pages=233, 382}}</ref>，並興建了新的教學大樓，亦吸納了更多學生<ref name="Dunbar1"/>。

大學課程漸趨職業導向，教學內容少了一些理論科學。可是，這所年輕的學府仍面臨財政危機，並受到管理層的關注。在這「波士頓理工」的歲月裡，學校的前教職員、時任[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]校長的[[查爾斯·艾略特|查爾斯·艾略特]]曾六度建議將麻省理工併入當時[[哈佛學院|哈佛學院]]的[[哈佛大学工程与应用科学学院|工程与应用科学学院]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/harvard-mit/index.html |title=Alumni Petition Opposing MIT-Harvard Merger, 1904–05 |publisher=Institute Archives, MIT |accessdate=10/01/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100722160408/https://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/harvard-mit/index.html |archive-date=2010-07-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=Alexander>{{cite web|last1=Alexander|first1=Philip N.|title=MIT-Harvard Rivalry Timeline|url=http://mta.scripts.mit.edu/CES/mit-harvard-rivalry-timeline/|website=MIT Music and Theater Arts News|publisher=Massachusetts Institute of Technology|accessdate=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714173624/http://mta.scripts.mit.edu/CES/mit-harvard-rivalry-timeline/|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。位於狹窄的後灣區的麻省理工學院無法負擔進一步的校園擴展費用，而學生的人數卻不斷上升，使之日趨擁擠。學校急需基金或捐款以維持正常運作。最終，校方在師生、校友的強烈反對下接受了與哈佛合併的邀請，惟1917年-{zh:麻省;zh-hk:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞州;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞州;}-最高法院以反大學壟斷的理由禁止了此舉，結束了這場「合併風波」<ref name="Alexander"/>。

1916年，麻省理工學院遷移至查爾斯河劍橋市的岸邊，沿岸伸延逾{{convert|1|mi|km|1}}，此為[[填海|填海]]土地<ref name=new_campus>{{cite web|title=Souvenir Program, Dedication of Cambridge Campus, 1916|url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/pageant/index.html|work=Object of the Month|publisher=MIT Institute Archives & Special Collections|accessdate=2012-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510124840/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/pageant/index.html|archive-date=2012-05-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite map |publisher=J. B. Shields |title=Middlesex Canal (Massachusetts) map, 1852 |url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Middlesex_Canal_%28Massachusetts%29_map,_1852.jpg |year=1852 |accessdate=2010-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101004104816/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Middlesex_Canal_(Massachusetts)_map,_1852.jpg |archive-date=2010-10-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這充滿[[新古典主義建築|新古典主義建築]]風格的「新理工」校園，由建築師{{link-en|威廉·W·博斯沃思|William W. Bosworth}}設計，受惠於一位匿名「好心人」的捐助，這位先生自1912年起便一直向校方提供資金<ref>{{cite web|title=Freeman's 1912 Design for the "New Technology"|url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/freeman/index.html|work=Object of the Month|publisher=MIT Institute Archives & Special Collections|accessdate=2012-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527195219/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/freeman/index.html|archive-date=2012-05-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。1920年1月，這位「好心人」的身份曝光——是來自[[羅徹斯特_(紐約州)|紐約州-{zh:羅徹斯特; zh-hans:罗切斯特; zh-hant:羅徹斯特;}-市]]的工業家[[喬治·伊士曼|喬治·伊士曼]]。他發明了新的電影製作及編輯方法，並成立了[[伊士曼柯達公司|伊士曼柯達公司]]。1912至1920年期間，伊士曼向麻省理工學院提供了兩千萬美金（現值兩億三千多萬）的現鈔及柯達的股票<ref>{{cite web |last=Lindsay |first=David |year=2000 |url=http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/amex/eastman/peopleevents/pande15.html |publisher=PBS-WGBH |title=Eastman Becomes a Mystery Donor to MIT |access-date=2015-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924153821/http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/amex/eastman/peopleevents/pande15.html |archive-date=2015-09-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===課程重整===
上世紀三十年代，校長[[卡爾·泰勒·康普頓|卡爾·泰勒·康普頓]]及副校長（職位等同{{link-en|教務長|Provost (education)}}）[[萬尼瓦爾·布殊|萬尼瓦爾·布殊]]重新提倡純科學（如[[物理學|物理學]]、[[化學|化學]]）的重要性，並減少了職業訓練成分<ref name="Lecuyer">{{cite journal|last=Lecuyer |first=Christophe |title=The making of a science based technological university: Karl Compton, James Killian, and the reform of MIT, 1930–1957 |journal=Historical Studies in the Physical and Biological Sciences |volume=23 |issue=1 |year=1992 |pages=153–180 |doi=10.2307/27757693}}</ref>。與[[常春藤盟校|常春藤盟校]]不同，麻省理工的學生主要來自中產階層，學校的經費多來自學費而非[[基金|捐款回贈]]<ref>{{cite book|first=Roger L. |last=Geiger |title=To advance knowledge: the growth of American research universities, 1900–1940 |year=2004 |pages=13–15, 179–9|isbn=0-19-503803-7}}</ref>。大學最終於1934年獲選入[[美國學院與大學協會|美國學院與大學協會]]<ref name="AAU">{{cite web|title=Member Institutions and Years of Admission|url=http://www.aau.edu/about/default.aspx?id=5476|publisher=Association of American Universities|accessdate=2012-06-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028050512/http://www.aau.edu/about/default.aspx?id=5476|archivedate=2012-10-28}}</ref>。

根據1949年的路易斯委員會報告，麻省理工學院「仍被廣泛認為是一所職業導向學校」，這亦是委員會希望改善的「不太合理之現象」。有關委員會全面地研究了學校的本科課程，建議校方提升多元性，並避免讓工程學或政府津貼的研究項目過於遠離文理學<ref name="MITTECHNOLOGYREVIEW">{{cite web|author=Bourzac, Katherine|url=http://www.technologyreview.com/printer_friendly_article.aspx?id=18345|title=Rethinking an MIT Education: The faculty reconsiders the General Institute Requirements|publisher=''[[科技創業|Technology Review]]''|date=03/12/2007}}</ref>。人文藝術與社會科學院及[[麻省理工斯隆管理學院|斯隆管理學院]]均於1950年成立，與發展完善的[[麻省理工理學院|理學院]]及[[麻省理工工程學院|工程學院]]互相競爭。本被邊緣化的經濟、管理、政治、語言學系開始力爭上游，並吸引了在學界廣受尊重的教授前來授課，更開辦了研究生課程<ref name="SchoolOfHASS">{{cite web |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/histories-offices/sch-hum.html |title=History: School of Humanities, Arts, and Social Sciences |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100311064018/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/histories-offices/sch-hum.html |archivedate=2010-03-11 |publisher=MIT Archives |accessdate=2008-07-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SloanSchool">{{cite web|url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/histories-offices/sch-sloan.html|title=History: Sloan School of Management|accessdate=2008-07-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100621002719/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/histories-offices/sch-sloan.html|archivedate=2010-06-21|publisher=MIT Archives|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|侯活·韋斯利·約翰遜|Howard Wesley Johnson|-{zh:侯活;zh-cn:霍华德;zh-hk:侯活;zh-tw:霍華;}-·韋斯利·約翰遜}}（1966年）及[[杰羅姆·威斯納|杰羅姆·威斯納]]（1980年）任職校長期間，學校進一步強調[[人文|人文]]的重要性，人文藝術與社會科學院得以繼續發展<ref>{{cite book |last=Johnson |first=Howard Wesley |url=http://www.google.com/books?id=9qpmDJQPEZEC&printsec=frontcover |title=Holding the Center: Memoirs of a Life in Higher Education |publisher=MIT Press |year=2001 |isbn=0-262-60044-7 |access-date=2015-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111222190322/http://www.google.com/books?id=9qpmDJQPEZEC&printsec=frontcover |archive-date=2011-12-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===軍事研究===
{{Quote box
 |align = right
 |quote = ......為一所圍繞科學、工程及文藝的教育機構。它的辦學宗旨使之定性為大學，<br>但它所涉獵的深度及廣度卻絕不限於此。
 |source = ——{{small|麻省理工學院校長{{link-en|詹姆斯·賴恩·基利安|James Rhyne Killian}}，1949年<ref name=Killian>{{cite web|last=Killian|first=James Rhyne|title=The Obligations and Ideals of an Institute of Technology|url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/inaugurations/killian.html|work=The Inaugural Address|publisher=Massachusetts Institute of Technology|accessdate=08/10/2013|date=04/02/1949|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141003061248/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/inaugurations/killian.html|archive-date=2014-10-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>}}
 |fontsize = big
 |salign = right
}}
麻省理工學院的{{link-en|軍事技術發展史|History of military technology|軍事科研活動}}隨著[[二戰|二戰]]的爆發而漸趨頻密。1941年，[[萬尼瓦爾·布殊|萬尼瓦爾·布殊]]獲委任為[[科學研究與發展部_(美國)|科研發展部長]]，負責分配資金給包括麻省理工在內的少數獲選定的大學<ref name="Zachary1">{{cite book |last=Zachary|first=Gregg |title=Endless Frontier: Vannevar Bush, Engineer of the American Century |url=https://archive.org/details/endlessfrontierv00zach|publisher= Free Press |year=1997 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/endlessfrontierv00zach/page/248 248]–249 |isbn = 0-684-82821-9}}</ref>。大戰期間，全國的科學家與工程學家聚集在1940年成立的{{link-en|麻省理工學院放射實驗室|Radiation Laboratory (MIT)|麻省理工放射實驗室}}，協助{{link-en|第二次世界大戰英國軍事史|Military history of the United Kingdom during World War II|英國軍方}}發展[[多腔磁控管|多腔磁控管]][[雷達|雷達]]技術，對整個戰爭影響甚大，亦塑造了戰後的研究方向<ref name="RadLab">{{cite web |url=http://www.ieeeghn.org/wiki/index.php/MIT_Rad_Lab |title=MIT's Rad Lab |publisher=IEEE Global History Network |accessdate=2008-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100707101603/http://www.ieeeghn.org/wiki/index.php/MIT_Rad_Lab |archive-date=2010-07-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。於{{link-en|查爾斯·斯塔克·德雷珀|Charles Stark Draper}}{{link-en|查爾斯·斯塔克·德雷珀實驗室|Charles Stark Draper Laboratory|儀表實驗室}}內進行的[[陀螺儀|陀螺儀]]、[[照準器|照準器]]、{{link-en|投彈瞄準器|Bombsight}}及[[慣性導航系統|慣性導航系統]]的[[控制系統|監控機制]]研究項目<ref>{{cite web|title=Doc Draper & His Lab|url=http://www.draper.com/doc_draper.html|work=History|publisher=The Charles Stark Draper Laboratory, Inc.|accessdate=2012-05-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527165103/http://www.draper.com/doc_draper.html|archivedate=2012-05-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Charles Draper: Gyroscopic Apparatus |url=http://web.mit.edu/invent/iow/draper.html |work=Inventor of the Week |publisher=MIT School of Engineering |accessdate=2012-05-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120418051730/http://web.mit.edu/invent/iow/draper.html |archivedate=2012-04-18 }}</ref>，[[旋風計算機|旋風計算機]]中的模擬飛行[[電腦|電腦]]系統<ref>{{cite web|title=Project Whirlwind|url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/project-whirlwind/index.html|work=Object of the Month|publisher=MIT Institute Archives & Special Collections|accessdate=2012-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120530075248/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/project-whirlwind/index.html|archive-date=2012-05-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，由{{link-en|哈羅德·金頓|Harold Eugene Edgerton}}指導的[[高速攝影|高速攝影]]、{{link-en|間諜氣球|Espionage balloon}}開發等<ref>{{cite web |url=http://edgerton-digital-collections.org/docs-life/wartime-strobe |accessdate=2009-11-28 |title=Wartime Strobe: 1939–1945 – Harold "Doc" Edgerton (Doc's Life) |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210111947/http://edgerton-digital-collections.org/docs-life/wartime-strobe |archive-date=2010-02-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Bedi |first=Joyce |title=MIT and World War II: Ingredients for a Hot Spot of Invention |url=http://invention.smithsonian.org/downloads/e-prototype_may10.pdf |accessdate=2012-05-30 |newspaper=Prototype |date=2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120524014558/http://invention.smithsonian.org/downloads/e-prototype_may10.pdf |archivedate=2012-05-24 }}</ref>，均為其他主要的軍事研究項目。大戰過後，麻省理工成為了全美最大型的戰時研發商（因而惹來了一些批評）<ref name="Zachary1"/>，僅是放射實驗室就聘請了四千名工作人員<ref name="RadLab"/>。截至1946年，全校剩餘了約一億（現值十二億）美元的資助金。可是，軍事研究並沒有因二戰的終結而結束。[[賢者系統|賢者系統]]、[[彈道導彈|彈道導彈]]、[[阿波羅計劃|阿波羅計劃]]等均為麻省理工戰後的政府資助研究項目<ref>{{cite book |last=Leslie |first=Stuart |title = The Cold War and American Science: The Military-Industrial-Academic Complex at MIT and Stanford |publisher=Columbia University Press |year=1993 |isbn=0-231-07959-1}}</ref>。

這些科研都深深影響著大學的發展。一份1949年的報告指校方「沒有因戰爭的結束而放慢校內的工作步伐」，並憶述了學校在戰前的那段「平靜的歲月」，但報告也承認大學對軍事發展的貢獻，並贊同校內師生人數、設施及研究課程確因發展軍事項目而得以提升<ref name=report_1949>{{cite report|url=https://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/pdf/lewis.pdf|author=MIT|year=1949|title=Report of The Committee on Educational Survey|access-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619204650/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/pdf/lewis.pdf|archive-date=2015-06-19|dead-url=yes|date=}}</ref>。在[[卡爾·泰勒·康普頓|卡爾·泰勒·康普頓]]（1930-1948年校長）、{{link-en|詹姆斯·賴恩·基利安|James Rhyne Killian}}（1948-1957年校長）及{{link-en|朱利葉·斯·力通|Julius Adams Stratton}}（1952-1957年校監）的帶領下，麻省理工的教職員及研究生人數分別上升了兩倍及五倍。他們的校園擴建策略為大學進一步的成長寫下了藍圖<ref name=report_1949/>。

到了上世紀六十至七十年代初，國內反戰者抗議美方參與[[越戰|越戰]]及麻省理工繼續進行軍事研究<ref name="Ins and outs">{{cite news|title=The 'Ins' and 'Outs' at M.I.T |work=The New York Times |date=1969-05-18 |last=Todd |first=Richard}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,900700,00.html |title=A Policy of Protest |date=1969-02-28 |accessdate=2008-08-13 |magazine=[[時代雜誌|Time]] |author1= |journal= |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081214153106/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,900700,00.html |archive-date=2008-12-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1969年3月4日，在一次師生會談後，校方決定成立{{link-en|科學家關注聯盟|Union of Concerned Scientists}}，旨在研究如何將學校的發展重點，從軍事轉移至環境及社會問題範疇<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ucsusa.org/ucs/about/founding-document-1968-mit-faculty-statement.html |title=Founding Document: 1968 MIT Faculty Statement |accessdate=08/12/2008 |publisher=Union of Concerned Scientists, USA |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080115200053/http://www.ucsusa.org/ucs/about/founding-document-1968-mit-faculty-statement.html |archivedate=2008-01-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終，麻省理工退出了儀表實驗室公司，並將所有的研究項目轉交給位於校外的[[麻省理工學院林肯實驗室|林肯實驗室]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Tension Over Issue of Defense Research |first=Fred |last=Hechinger|date=11/09/1969 |work=The New York Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| title=MIT Curb on Secret Projects Reflects Growing Antimilitary Feeling Among Universities' Researchers |first=William |last=Stevens |date=1969-05-05 |work=The New York Times}}</ref>。在這期間，校內並沒有出現大的騷動，全校師生基本團結一致<ref name="Ins and outs"/>，而約翰遜亦因領導有方而獲得讚賞<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1999/johnson-0609.html |title=A tribute to MIT's Howard Johnson |first=David |last=Warsh |work=The Boston Globe |date=06/01/1999 |accessdate=2007-04-04 |quote=At a critical time in the late 1960s, Johnson stood up to the forces of campus rebellion at MIT. Many university presidents were destroyed by the troubles. Only Edward Levi, University of Chicago president, had comparable success guiding his institution to a position of greater strength and unity after the turmoil. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100124183736/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1999/johnson-0609.html |archive-date=2010-01-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===近年要事===
[[File:MIT_Media_Lab.jpg|thumb]]內的工作人員致力發掘電腦科技的新用途。圖中的大樓建於1982年，由[[貝聿銘|貝聿銘]]設計；右邊延伸的部分則由[[槙文彥|槙文彥]]設計，並於2010年正式啟用。]]
[[File:Heckert_GNU_white.svg|upright]]及[[自由軟件運動|自由軟件運動]]。]]
麻省理工學院亦與數碼年代的發展息息相關。除了現代-{zh:電腦;zh-cn:电子计算机;zh-hk:電腦; zh-tw:電腦}-及[[電腦網絡|-{zh:電腦;zh-cn:电子计算机;zh-hk:電腦; zh-tw:電腦}-網絡]]的先驅<ref>{{cite journal |last=Lee |first=J.A.N. |first2=J. |last2=McCarthy |first3=J.C.R. |last3=Licklider |title=The beginnings at MIT |journal=IEEE Annals of the History of Computing |year=1992 |volume=14 |issue=1 |pages=18–54 |doi=10.1109/85.145317 |url=http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/articleDetails.jsp?tp=&arnumber=145317&contentType=Journals+%26+Magazines&sortType%3Dasc_p_Sequence%26filter%3DAND%28p_IS_Number%3A3898%29 |accessdate=2012-05-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130220043833/http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/articleDetails.jsp?tp=&arnumber=145317&contentType=Journals+%26+Magazines&sortType%3Dasc_p_Sequence%26filter%3DAND%28p_IS_Number%3A3898%29 |archivedate=2013-02-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.computerhistory.org/internet_history/ |title=Internet History |publisher=Computer History Museum |accessdate=2008-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403115211/http://www.computerhistory.org/internethistory/ |archive-date=2017-04-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，大學的[[麻省理工電腦科學與人工智能實驗室|-{zh:電腦;zh-cn:电子计算机;zh-hk:電腦; zh-tw:電腦}-與人工智能實驗室]]及[[鐵路模型技術俱樂部|鐵路技術部]]還研發了一些早期的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]（例如「[[太空之戰_(電子遊戲)|太空之戰]]」），並創造了現代[[黑客|黑客]]的{{link-en|行話文件|Jargon File}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.catb.org/~esr/writings/cathedral-bazaar/hacker-history/ar01s02.html |title=A Brief History of Hackerdom |first=Eric S. |last=Raymond |accessdate=08/11/2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010145931/http://www.catb.org/~esr/writings/cathedral-bazaar/hacker-history/ar01s02.html |archive-date=2008-10-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。除此，不少電腦技術機構均起源於麻省理工學院，這包括了八十年代由[[理查·斯托曼|-{zh-hans:理查德·斯托曼; zh-hk:理查·斯托曼;}-]]建立的「[[GNU計劃|GNU計劃]]」及後來的[[自由軟件基金會|自由軟件基金會]]，1985年由[[尼古拉斯·尼葛洛龐帝|尼古拉斯·尼葛洛龐帝]]與杰羅姆·威斯納創辦的[[麻省理工媒體實驗室|媒體實驗室]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.media.mit.edu/?page_id=16 |title=The Media Lab – Retrospective |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090417085247/http://media.mit.edu/?page_id=16 |archivedate=2009-04-17 |publisher=MIT Media Lab |accessdate=08/12/2008 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1994年由[[提姆·柏內茲-李|提姆·柏內茲-李]]建立的[[標準組織|標準組織]][[萬維網聯盟|萬維網聯盟]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.w3.org/Consortium/facts#history |title=About W3C: History |accessdate=08/11/2008 |publisher=World Wide Web Consortium |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091017060547/http://www.w3.org/Consortium/facts#history |archive-date=2009-10-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2002年開設的開放課程軟件<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ocw.mit.edu/|title=MIT OpenCourseWare|accessdate=06/12/2008|publisher=MIT|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080720060606/http://ocw.mit.edu/|archive-date=2008-07-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2005年創立的「[[OLPC|一童一電腦]]」計劃等<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.laptop.org/en/vision/mission/ |title=Mission – One Laptop Per Child |publisher=One Laptop Per Child |accessdate=08/11/2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080813080949/http://laptop.org/en/vision/mission/ |archive-date=2008-08-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

大學分別在1976及1989年獲賦予「海洋資助大學」與「太空資助大學」的銜頭，獲給予支援進行海洋科學及航空與航天的研究工作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/masgc/www/index.shtml |title=Massachusetts Space Grant Consortium |accessdate=2008-08-26 |publisher=Massachusetts Space Grant Consortium |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080916130459/http://web.mit.edu/masgc/www/index.shtml |archive-date=2008-09-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://seagrant.mit.edu/about_us/index.php|title=MIT Sea Grant College Program|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090404013114/http://seagrant.mit.edu/about_us/index.php|archivedate=2009-04-04|accessdate=2008-08-26|publisher=MIT Sea Grant College Program|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。雖然政府的資助在過去的四分之一個世紀裡有所減少，但校方發動了幾次[[籌款|籌款]]活動，效果不俗。學校增添了西部校園新宿舍與體育設施，東北角的[[生物學|生物學]]、[[神經科學|腦與認知科學]]、[[遺傳學|遺傳學]]、[[生物技術|生物技術]]及[[癌症|癌症]]研究中心，瓦薩街的[[史塔特科技中心|史塔特科技中心]]等「外景」建築，及[[麻省理工學院校園|唐氏管理學教育中心]]<ref>{{Cite book |last = Simha. |first = O. R. |title = MIT campus planning 1960–2000: An annotated chronology |year = 2003 |pages = 120–149 |url = http://books.google.com/?id=ldq-ZgxszzMC&lpg=PA120&pg=PA120| isbn = 978-0-262-69294-6 |publisher = MIT Press}}</ref>。千禧後，媒體實驗室、斯隆學院東部校園及西北研究生宿舍均獲得擴建<ref>{{cite web|url=http://web.mit.edu/facilities/construction/ki/index.html|title=MIT Facilities: In Development & Construction|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312070340/http://web.mit.edu/facilities/construction/ki/index.html|archivedate=2009-03-12|publisher=MIT|accessdate=2008-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/news/nation/articles/2006/09/14/mit_will_accelerate_its_building_boom/ |title=MIT will accelerate its building boom: $750m expansion to add 4 facilities |last=Bombardieri |first=Marcella |date=2006-09-14 |work=The Boston Globe |accessdate=2008-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724211852/http://www.boston.com/news/nation/articles/2006/09/14/mit_will_accelerate_its_building_boom/ |archive-date=2008-07-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年，校長霍克菲爾德成立了麻省理工能源研究協會。此乃跨學科機構，旨在探索由[[世界能源消耗量|能源消耗]]所帶來的挑戰及解決辦法<ref>{{cite web|title=About MITEI|url=http://web.mit.edu/mitei/about/index.html|publisher=MIT Energy Initiative|accessdate=2012-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120504143032/http://web.mit.edu/mitei/about/index.html|archive-date=2012-05-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2001年，受到{{link-en|支持開放資源運動|Open-source movement}}的啟發<ref>{{cite news |title=Get it out in the open |last=Attwood |first=Rebecca |date=2009-09-24 |url=http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?storycode=408300 |newspaper=''Times Higher Education'' |access-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121201130511/http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?storycode=408300 |archive-date=2012-12-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，麻省理工創立了[[開放式課程網頁|開放式課程網頁]]，作為放置免費公開課堂筆記、{{link-en|問題集|Problem set}}、課程大綱、測考試題及網上講堂的平台（惟不設任何課程認證）<ref>{{cite news |last=Goldberg |first=Carey |date=2001-04-04 |newspaper=The New York Times |title=Auditing Classes at M.I.T., on the Web and Free |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2001/04/04/us/auditing-classes-at-mit-on-the-web-and-free.html |access-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906021514/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/04/04/us/auditing-classes-at-mit-on-the-web-and-free.html |archive-date=2015-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然經費龐大，但有關計劃的規模不跌反升，不少其他大學自2005年起紛紛加入<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/04/18/education/edlife/18open-t.html |title=An Open Mind |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2010-04-16 |last=Hafner |first=Katie |access-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910194744/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/04/18/education/edlife/18open-t.html |archive-date=2015-09-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。發展至今，已有逾250所教育機構為此計劃的成員，有關物資共有六種語言版本<ref>{{cite news |title=For Exposure, Universities Put Courses on the Web |last=Guttenplan |first=D.D. |date=11/01/2010 |newspaper=The New York Times |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/01/world/europe/01iht-educLede01.html |access-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906033609/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/01/world/europe/01iht-educLede01.html |archive-date=2015-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年，麻省理工宣佈給予完成名為「MITx」網上課程的用戶相關證書（但非為學分或學位性質），有意者需繳付學費，價錢適中<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/19/education/mit-expands-free-online-courses-offering-certificates.html |last=Lewin |first=Tamar |date=2011-12-19 |newspaper=The New York Times |title=M.I.T. Expands Its Free Online Courses |access-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907005558/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/19/education/mit-expands-free-online-courses-offering-certificates.html |archive-date=2015-09-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。支援「MITx」的「[[edX|edX]]」平台由麻省理工與[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]一同研發（哈佛亦有自己的「Harvardx」系統）。已有不少其他大學通過「edX」上載自己的開放資源<ref>{{cite news |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2012/edx-faq-050212.html |title=What is edX? |publisher=MIT News Office |date=05/02/2012 |access-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228034856/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2012/edx-faq-050212.html |archive-date=2014-02-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年4月，[[波士頓馬拉松爆炸案|波士頓馬拉松爆炸案]]事發三天後，麻省理工警衛肖恩·科利爾被疑犯開槍射死。大規模的搜捕行動因而展開，校園及波士頓市中心被封鎖了一天<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/25/us/officers-killing-spurred-pursuit-in-boston-attack.html |title=Officer's Killing Spurred Pursuit in Boston Attack |date=2013-04-24 |publisher=''The New York Times'' |last1=Ruderman |first1=Wendy |last2=Kovaleski |first2=Serge |last3=Cooper |first3=Michael |access-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928180836/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/25/us/officers-killing-spurred-pursuit-in-boston-attack.html |archive-date=2015-09-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。共有逾一萬人參與了一週後的科利爾悼念活動，出席者包括了上千名來自[[新英格蘭|新英格蘭]]及[[加拿大|加拿大]]地區的警員<ref name=Bidgood>{{cite news|last=Bidgood|first=Jess|title=On a Field at M.I.T., 10,000 Remember an Officer Who Was Killed|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/25/us/boston-marathon-bombings-developments.html?_r=0|accessdate=2014-01-30|newspaper=New York Times|date=2013-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722022602/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/25/us/boston-marathon-bombings-developments.html?_r=0|archive-date=2013-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Faviero>{{cite news |last=Faviero |first=Bruno B. F. |title=Thousands attend Sean Collier memorial service |url=http://tech.mit.edu/V133/N21/memorial.html |accessdate=2014-01-30 |newspaper=''The Tech'' |volume=133 |number=21 |date=2013-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219121813/http://tech.mit.edu/V133/N21/memorial.html |archive-date=2014-02-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57581186/thousands-attend-slain-mit-officers-memorial-service/ |title=Thousands attend slain MIT officer's memorial service |date=2013-04-24 |publisher=CBS News |access-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106123531/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57581186/thousands-attend-slain-mit-officers-memorial-service/ |archive-date=2013-11-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年11月25日，麻省理工宣佈開設年度的科利爾獎章，用以表揚「那些能體現科利爾警員的素養與精神的人」，獎項「不受職業所限」，「促進社區溝通並具一貫、無私的博愛精神」為獲獎的準則<ref name=MITNCM>{{cite news|title=Letter regarding the establishment of the Collier Medal|url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2013/letter-collier-medal-1125.html|accessdate=2013-11-26|newspaper=MIT News|date=2013-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203114833/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2013/letter-collier-medal-1125.html|archive-date=2013-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=MITCM>{{cite web|title=Collier Medal|url=http://police.mit.edu/collier-medal|work=MIT Police|publisher=MIT|accessdate=2013-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203123746/http://police.mit.edu/collier-medal|archive-date=2013-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Rocheleau>{{cite news|last=Rocheleau|first=Matt|title=MIT to establish a Sean Collier award|url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/metro/2013/11/26/mit-establish-annual-award-memory-slain-officer-sean-collier/v3T1hn3Oi7ObLVE9hOm6GP/story.html|accessdate=2013-11-26|newspaper=The Boston Globe|date=2013-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202223917/http://www.bostonglobe.com/metro/2013/11/26/mit-establish-annual-award-memory-slain-officer-sean-collier/v3T1hn3Oi7ObLVE9hOm6GP/story.html|archive-date=2013-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==校園環境==
{{Main|麻省理工學院校園}}
===格局概覽===
[[File:MIT_Main_Campus_Aerial.jpg|thumb]]空中俯瞰中央與東部校園。照片中央為面向基利安閣的大圓頂，背後為{{link-en|肯德爾廣場|Kendall Square}}。]]
{{multiple image
   | direction = horizontal
   | width1     = 100
   | width2     = 200
   | align     = left
   | footer    =位於{{link-en|麻省大道 (波士頓市區)|Massachusetts Avenue (metropolitan Boston)|-{zh:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞;zh-hk:麻省;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞;}-大道}}77號的七號大廳（左）被認為是學校的入口，而 [[無盡長廊|無盡長廊]]（右）則是進入整座校園的主要通道。
   | image1    = MIT Lobby 7.jpg
   | image2    = Infinitecorridor.jpg}}

麻省理工學院佔地{{convert|168|acre|ha|1|sing=on}}的校園坐落於[[查爾斯河|查爾斯河]]以北一英里的[[劍橋_(麻省)|劍橋市]]，由{{link-en|麻省大道 (波士頓市區)|Massachusetts Avenue (metropolitan Boston)|-{zh:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞;zh-hk:麻省;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞;}-大道}}分為東西兩區<ref name="Campus"/>。不少的學生宿舍及活動設施位於西面，而多數的學術大樓則在東面。沿著{{link-en|麻省大道 (波士頓市區)|Massachusetts Avenue (metropolitan Boston)|-{zh:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞;zh-hk:麻省;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞;}-大道}}而起的七號大樓被認為是[[無盡長廊|無盡長廊]]及整所學府的入口<ref name="BO"/>。[[哈佛大橋|哈佛大橋]]是最為靠近的橋樑，此橋以[[斯穆特|斯穆特]]（非正規單位）劃結，是麻省理工學生的惡作劇之一<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.technologyreview.com/article/20983/ |title=Smoot's Legacy: 50th anniversary of famous feat nears |accessdate=2008-08-13 |magazine=Technology Review|last=Durant |first=Elizabeth}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=The Measure of This Man Is in the Smoot; MIT's Human Yardstick Honored for Work |work=The Washington Post |date=12/08/2005 |last=Fahrenthold |first=David}}</ref>。{{link-en|麻省灣紅線鐵路|Red Line (MBTA)|-{zh:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞;zh-hk:麻省;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞;}-灣紅線鐵路}}{{link-en|肯德爾/麻省理工鐵路站|Kendall/MIT (MBTA station)|肯德爾/麻省理工站}}位於{{link-en|肯德爾廣場|Kendall Square}}校園的東北邊界。麻省理工校園周圍高科技公司林立，它們有的為現代化辦公大樓，也有的為重建的工業大廈。除此，也能找到具不同樓價的住宅社區<ref>{{cite web|title=Cambridge: Just the Facts (City Facts Brochure)|url=http://www.cambridgema.gov|publisher=City of Cambridge|accessdate=2012-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110223044204/http://cambridgema.gov/|archive-date=2011-02-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="BO">{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/catalog/overv.chap1.html |title=MIT Course Catalogue: Overview |publisher=MIT |accessdate=2008-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090810214438/http://web.mit.edu/catalog/overv.chap1.html |archive-date=2009-08-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

每一棟大樓都有一個編號（前面或有''「W」''、''「N」''、''「E」''或''「NW」''四個用以標示方位的英文字母），亦有自己的名稱。一般而言，人們多以編號稱呼學術或辦公大樓，名稱稱呼學生宿舍。編號大致是按照每座大樓面世的先後次序，以及它們與中央校園麥克勞林建築群的距離分配<ref name="Numbering system">{{cite web |url=http://studentlife.mit.edu/mindandhandbook/campus-life/building-history |title=Building History and Numbering System |publisher=Mind and Hand Book, MIT |accessdate=2008-08-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101222150052/http://studentlife.mit.edu/mindandhandbook/campus-life/building-history |archivedate=2010-12-22 }}</ref>。除了地面走道，地下也有不少連接各個大樓的隧道，方便人們躲開惡劣天氣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mit.edu/facilities/maps/tunnelMap.pdf|format=PDF|title=MIT Campus Subterranean Map|publisher=MIT Department of Facilities|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100731034447/http://mit.edu/facilities/maps/tunnelMap.pdf|archivedate=2010-07-31|accessdate=2008-08-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title='Hackers' Skirt Security in Late-Night MIT Treks |newspaper=The Boston Globe|last=Abel |first=David |date=2000-03-30}}</ref>。

麻省理工學院的{{link-en|麻省理工核能研究反應堆|MIT Nuclear Research Reactor|校園核能研究反應堆}}為全美最强大的大學[[核反應堆|核反應堆]]之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/catalogue/overv.chap6-nrl.shtml |title=MIT Course Catalogue |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104182125/http://web.mit.edu/catalogue/overv.chap6-nrl.shtml |archivedate=2009-01-04 |publisher=MIT |accessdate=2008-07-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不過，此設施因非常接近民居而惹來了一些爭議<ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/LooseNukes/ |title=Loose Nukes: A Special Report |publisher=ABC News |accessdate=2007-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028073010/http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/LooseNukes/ |archive-date=2009-10-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。校方一再強調，有關設施的保安系統非常完善，不會有安全問題<ref>{{cite news |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2005/reactor.html |title=MIT Assures Community of Research Reactor Safety |publisher=MIT News Office |date=2005-10-13 |accessdate=10/05/2006 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051221004207/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2005/reactor.html |archive-date=2005-12-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1999年，[[比爾·蓋茨|比爾·蓋茨]]向麻省理工捐助了兩千萬美金建造名為「威廉·H·蓋茨大樓」的電腦實驗室，此建築物由[[法蘭克·蓋瑞|-{zh:法蘭克·蓋瑞;zh-hans:弗兰克·盖里;zh-hant:法蘭克·蓋瑞;}-]]設計。雖然[[微軟公司|微軟公司]]亦曾向校方提供捐款，但這是比爾·蓋茨首次以私人名譽提供資金<ref>{{cite web|title=Bill Gates Donates $20 million to MIT|url=http://www.thecrimson.com/article/1999/4/14/bill-gates-donates-20-million-to/|work=The Harvard Crimson|publisher=The Harvard Crimson, Inc|accessdate=06/04/2014|author=Matthew G.H. Chun|date=1999-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407070541/http://www.thecrimson.com/article/1999/4/14/bill-gates-donates-20-million-to/|archive-date=2014-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他著名校園建築包括了加壓[[風洞|風洞]]及{{link-en|船模水池|Ship model basin}}，用以測試海上船隻或設備模型<ref>{{cite news|title=Supersonic Tunnel Open; Naval Laboratory for Aircraft Dedicated at M.I.T |work=The New York Times |date=12/02/1949}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Ship Test Tank for M.I.T.; Dr. Killian Announces Plant to Cost $500,000 |work=The New York Times |date=02/06/1949}}</ref>。

麻省理工的無線網絡覆蓋全校園（面積達{{convert|9400000|sqft|m2}}）。此系統於2005年面世，共有近三千個連接點<ref>{{cite web |url=http://senseable.mit.edu/news/on_us/CNN4November2005.htm |title=MIT maps wireless users across campus |date=2005-11-04 |accessdate=2007-03-03 |publisher=MIT |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060905081952/http://senseable.mit.edu/news/on_us/CNN4November2005.htm |archivedate=2006-09-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2001年，[[美國國家環境保護局|美國國家環境保護局]]就麻省理工的{{link-en|危險廢物|Hazardous waste}}處置方法提出訴訟，指校方違反了{{link-en|水淨化法例 (美國)|Clean Water Act|《水淨化法例》}}及{{link-en|空氣淨化法例 (美國)|Clean Air Act (United States)|《空氣淨化法例》}}<ref name="EPA">{{cite web |url=http://www.epa.gov/EPA-WATER/2001/May/Day-03/w11123.htm |title=Notice of Lodging of Consent Decree Pursuant to the Resource Conservation and Recovery Act, the Clean Air Act, and the Clean Water Act |publisher=Environmental Protection Agency |date=05/03/2001 |accessdate=2008-07-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081225093324/http://www.epa.gov/EPA-WATER/2001/May/Day-03/w11123.htm |archivedate=2008-12-25 }}</ref>。學校最終被罰款15.5萬美金，後制定了三項環境改善方針<ref>{{cite news |title=MIT to create three new environmental projects as part of agreement with EPA |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/epa-0425.html |publisher=MIT News Office |date=04/212001 |first=Robert |last=Sales |accessdate=2008-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080302043137/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/epa-0425.html |archive-date=2008-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了發動校園擴建籌款活動，校方還籌備了資金重新設計各個大樓，以提高它們的能源效益。[[替代燃料|替代燃料]]校車、公共交通資助、熱電廠建設（提供校園電力及熱能）等均為學校為減少環境破壞而推出的額外措施<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/environment/commitment/conservation.html |title=The Environment at MIT: Conservation |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104133307/http://web.mit.edu/environment/commitment/conservation.html |archivedate=2009-01-04 |publisher=MIT |accessdate=08/11/2008 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

麻省理工警衛部、地區及州警察局於2009-2011年期間，共接獲的校園罪案包括：12宗性罪案、6宗搶劫案、3宗襲擊案、164宗盗窃案、1宗縱火案、4宗電單車盜竊案，共牽涉22,000位學生及學校職員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.american-school-search.com/safety/massachusetts-institute-of-technology |title=Safety & Crime Report – Massachusetts Institute of Technology |publisher=American School Search |accessdate=2013-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002225750/http://www.american-school-search.com/safety/massachusetts-institute-of-technology |archive-date=2013-10-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===建築風格===
{{multiple image
   | direction = horizontal
   | width1     = 200
   | width2     = 245
   | align     = left
   | footer    = 麻省理工學院十號大樓與大圓頂。
   | image1    = MIT Building 10 and the Great Dome, Cambridge MA.jpg
   | image2    = MIT Dome night1 Edit.jpg}}
[[File:Wfm_stata_center.jpg|right]]為麻省理工-{zh:電腦;zh-cn:计算机;zh-hk:電腦;zh-tw:電腦;}-科學與人工智能實驗室、資訊與決策系統實驗室及語言與哲學系的所在地。]]
麻省理工建築與規劃學院是全美第一所建築學院<ref>{{cite web |url=http://architecture.mit.edu/welcome.html |title=MIT Architecture: Welcome |accessdate=2007-04-04 |publisher=MIT Department of Architecture |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070323150619/http://architecture.mit.edu/welcome.html |archivedate=2007-03-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，一直以來設計了不少風格前衛的建築物<ref name="Starchitecture">{{cite news |title=Starchitecture on Campus |url=http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2004/02/22/starchitecture_on_campus/ |date=2004-02-22 |accessdate=2006-10-24 |work=The Boston Globe |first=David |last=Dillon |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061005063337/http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2004/02/22/starchitecture_on_campus/ |archive-date=2006-10-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=At MIT, Going Boldly Where No Architect Has Gone Before |last=Flint |first=Anthony |date=2002-10-13 |work=The Boston Globe}}</ref>。第一批建於劍橋校園的大樓常被稱之為「麥克勞林建築群」，因它們是在校長{{link-en|理查德·科伯恩·麥克勞林|Richard Cockburn Maclaurin}}的監督下完工。這些由建築學大師{{link-en|威廉·W·博斯沃思|William W. Bosworth}}設計的大樓，是全美第一批以[[鋼筋混凝土|鋼筋混凝土]]建成的非工業建築物<ref name="Jarzombek1">{{Cite book|last=Jarzombek |first=Mark|title=Designing MIT: Bosworth's New Tech |place=Boston |year=2004 |publisher=Northeastern University Press |pages=50–51 |url=http://books.google.com/?id=QiwRGc3E7Z8C&printsec=frontcover |isbn=978-1-55553-619-0}}</ref>。博斯沃思的設計靈感來自二十世紀初的[[城市美化運動|城市美化運動]]，並參照了[[萬神廟|萬神廟]]的風格建造內含巴克工程學圖書館的大圓頂<ref name="Jarzombek1"/>。大圓頂面向每年畢業典禮的舉辦地點——基利安閣。周邊的石灰石大樓刻有一些重要的科學家與哲學家之名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/names/index.html |title=Names of MIT Buildings |publisher=MIT Archives |accessdate=04/10/2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100519104929/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/names/index.html |archive-date=2010-05-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=TechNames>{{cite news|title=Names on Institute Buildings Lend Inspiration to Future Scientists|url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/names/the-tech.html|accessdate=2015-05-30|newspaper=''The Tech''|volume=XLII|number=70|date=1922-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013722/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/names/the-tech.html|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[阿爾瓦爾·阿爾托|阿爾瓦爾·阿爾托]]所設計的巴克舍（1947年）、[[埃羅·沙里寧|埃羅·沙里寧]]的麻省理工教堂與克雷斯吉禮堂（1955年）、[[貝聿銘|貝聿銘]]的{{link-en|麻省理工格林大樓|Green Building (MIT)|格林大樓}}、德雷福斯、朗多、威斯納大樓均獲譽為是二戰後[[現代主義建築|現代化建築風格]]的標杆<ref>{{cite news|title=Colleges: More Than Ivy-Covered Halls |date=03/02/1986 |last=Campbell |first=Robert |work=The Boston Globe}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,889750,00.html |title=Challenge to the Rectangle |work=TIME Magazine |accessdate=2008-08-13 |date=1953-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081222124045/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,889750,00.html |archive-date=2008-12-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,869832,00.html |title=Flagpole in the Square |work=TIME Magazine |date=1960-08-22 |accessdate=2008-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090114202627/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,869832,00.html |archive-date=2009-01-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一些諸如[[法蘭克·蓋瑞|-{zh:法蘭克·蓋瑞;zh-hans:弗兰克·盖里;zh-hant:法蘭克·蓋瑞;}-]]的[[史塔特科技中心|史塔特科技中心]]（2004年）、[[史蒂芬·霍爾|史蒂芬·霍爾]]的西蒙斯舍堂（2002年）、{{link-en|查爾斯·科雷亞|Charles Correa}}的四十六號大樓（2005年）、[[槙文彥|槙文彥]]的媒體實驗室等更為現代化的建築物，與波士頓區內的大片古典式建築大有不同<ref name="Starchitecture"/><ref>{{Cite news|title=Architecture's Brand Names Come to Town |work=The Boston Globe |date=2001-05-20 |last=Campbell |first=Robert}}</ref>。它們常獲稱之為「星級建築」<ref>{{cite news|title=The Campuses of Cambridge, A City Unto Themselves |last=Paul |first=James |work=The Washington Post |date=04/09/1989}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/11/23/AR2007112300679_pf.html |title=The Hubris of a Great Artist Can Be a Gift or a Curse |work=The Washington Post |last=Lewis |first=Roger K. |date=2007-11-24 |accessdate=2008-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112200924/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/11/23/AR2007112300679_pf.html |archive-date=2012-11-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；不過，2010年的[[普林斯頓評論|《普林斯頓評論》]]卻將之列入二十所「校園擁擠、不堪入目或兩者兼備」的名單之中<ref>{{cite web|title=2010 361 Best College Rankings: Quality of Life: Campus Is Tiny, Unsightly, or Both|url=http://www.princetonreview.com/schools/college/CollegeRankings.aspx?iid=1023832|publisher=''Princeton Review''|year=2010|accessdate=07/06/2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903002543/http://www.princetonreview.com/schools/college/CollegeRankings.aspx?iid=1023832|archive-date=2014-09-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==行政架構==
根據憲章，麻省理工學院為非牟利機構，由名為「麻省理工校董委員會」的私立[[董事會|董事會]]所管理<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/corporation/about.html |title=MIT Corporation |accessdate=2007-03-18 |publisher=MIT Corporation |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070222205618/http://web.mit.edu/corporation/about.html |archive-date=2007-02-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該委員會現設43席，每屆任期為五年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/corporation/membership/members-list.html |title=Members of the MIT Corporation: Term Members |publisher=The MIT Corporation |accessdate=09/07/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100803023512/http://web.mit.edu/corporation/membership/members-list.html |archive-date=2010-08-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其中，有25位為終身委員（在75歲前均有投票權）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/corporation/membership/life-members-list.html |title=Members of the MIT Corporation: Life Members |publisher=The MIT Corporation |accessdate=09/07/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100803023502/http://web.mit.edu/corporation/membership/life-members-list.html |archive-date=2010-08-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，3位直選委員（校長、財務秘書及行政秘書）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/corporation/membership/officers.html |title=Members of the MIT Corporation: Officers |publisher=The MIT Corporation |accessdate=09/07/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111023233853/http://web.mit.edu/corporation/membership/officers.html |archive-date=2011-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，4位當然委員（校友協會主席、{{link-en|麻省州長|Governor of Massachusetts|-{zh:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞;zh-hk:麻省;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞;}-州長}}、-{zh:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞;zh-hk:麻省;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞;}-教育部長、{{link-en|麻省最高法院|Massachusetts Supreme Judicial Court|-{zh:麻省;zh-cn:马萨诸塞;zh-hk:麻省;zh-tw:麻薩諸塞;}-最高法院}}大法官）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/corporation/membership/ex-officio-list.html |title=Members of the MIT Corporation: Ex Officio Members |publisher=The MIT Corporation |accessdate=09/07/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100803023452/http://web.mit.edu/corporation/membership/ex-officio-list.html |archive-date=2010-08-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/corporation/bylaws/by2.html |title=Bylaws of the MIT Corporation – Section 2: Members |publisher=The MIT Corporation |accessdate=09/07/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026145619/http://web.mit.edu/corporation/bylaws/by2.html |archive-date=2011-10-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。校董會負責批核學校的預算案與新課程草議，頒授學位，委任新入職教師與工作人員，及選出作最終行政決策的校長<ref name="BO"/><ref>{{cite web |title=A Brief History and Workings of the Corporation |url=http://web.mit.edu/fnl/volume/185/mead.html |accessdate=11/02/2006 |publisher=MIT Faculty Newsletter |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100426082614/http://web.mit.edu/fnl/volume/185/mead.html |archive-date=2010-04-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。麻省理工投資管理機構負責管理大學收到的捐款回贈及其他財務事宜<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mitimco.org/ |title=MIT Investment Management Company |accessdate=01/08/2007 |publisher=MIT Investment Management Company |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070119090122/http://www.mitimco.org/ |archive-date=2007-01-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。校方於2013-14年度共有逾124億美金的捐款，位列全美高校第六<ref name=NACOBU/>。

麻省理工共設六所學術學院：理學院、工程學院、建築學院、[[麻省理工斯隆管理學院|管理學院]]、人文藝術與社會科學院、[[哈佛-麻省理工醫療科技學院|醫療科技學院]]<ref name="Schools">{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/facts/academic.shtml |title=MIT Facts: Academic Schools and Departments, Divisions & Sections |year=2010 |accessdate=10/01/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080726011503/http://web.mit.edu/facts/academic.shtml |archive-date=2008-07-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然教職員委員會對學校的教研、學生活動安排、行政事務等多方面具實質控制權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://web.mit.edu/annualreports/pres05/17.00.pdf|format=PDF|author=Rafael L. Bras|title=Reports to the President, Report of the Chair of the Faculty|date=2004–2005|accessdate=12/01/2006|publisher=MIT|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090930142655/http://web.mit.edu/annualreports/pres05/17.00.pdf|archive-date=2009-09-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但那32位學系主任只向有關學院的院長負責，而院長則向對校長負責的教務長報告<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/orgchart/replist.html |title=Reporting List |publisher=MIT |accessdate=09/07/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100326141200/http://web.mit.edu/orgchart/replist.html |archive-date=2010-03-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==學術泛論==
===收生概況===
麻省理工學院為全美入學門欄最高、競爭最大的學府之一，具低轉入率<ref>{{cite web|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/mit-2178|title=Massachusetts Institute of Technology|publisher=''U.S.News & World Report''|date=2015|accessdate=2015-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905130625/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/mit-2178|archive-date=2015-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。校方共收到18,356個本科、19,446個研究生2014-15學年的入學申請，分別僅錄取了1,447（7.9%）及2,991（15.4%）名申請者，最終分別有1,043（72.1%）及1,880（62.8%）位獲青睞的學生選擇入讀此校。本科生[[SAT|SAT]]成績[[四分差|四分差]]為2090–2340（滿分2400）<ref name="Carnegie" /><ref name="Enrollment Statistics"/>。除了考試成績，校方亦重視課外活動、學校推薦信、面試表現等其他因素<ref name="Enrollment Statistics"/>。

===教學概論===
麻省理工學院為一所大型、具高住宿率的[[研究型大學|研究型大學]]，以研究或專業學科生居多<ref name="Carnegie">{{cite web|title=Massachusetts Institute of Technology|url=http://classifications.carnegiefoundation.org/lookup_listings/view_institution.php?unit_id=166683|publisher=Carnegie Foundation for the Advancement of Teaching|accessdate=10/01/2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140919133534/http://classifications.carnegiefoundation.org/lookup_listings/view_institution.php?unit_id=166683|archive-date=2014-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大學自1929年起就一直獲得[[新英格蘭學校與學院協會|新英格蘭學校與學院協會]]的{{link-en|教育認可|Educational accreditation}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/facts/accreditation.html |title=MIT Facts: Accreditation |publisher=MIT |accessdate=09/06/2010 |year=2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080813100857/http://web.mit.edu/facts/accreditation.html |archive-date=2008-08-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://cihe.neasc.org/about_our_institutions/roster_of_institutions/details/13437 |title=Roster of Institutions |publisher=Commission on Institutions of Higher Education, New England Association of Schools and Colleges |accessdate=09/06/2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106010359/http://cihe.neasc.org/about_our_institutions/roster_of_institutions/details/13437 |archivedate=2013-11-06 }}</ref>。麻省理工實行「4-1-4」學制：秋季學期始於每年的[[勞動節_(美國)|勞動節]]翌日，結束於十二月中旬，其後會有一個月的「自由活動」時間，二月初至五月底則為春季學期<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/registrar/calendar/index.html |title=Academic Calendar |publisher=Officer of the Registrar, MIT |accessdate=09/06/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100414185209/http://web.mit.edu/registrar/calendar/index.html |archive-date=2010-04-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

<!--學士教育-->
麻省理工的四年學士學位合計44種，由五所學院提供，專業及文理類別約各佔一半，2015年學費為46,704[[美金|美金]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/catalog/front.degre.html |title=MIT Course Catalog: Degree Charts |publisher=Officer of the Registrar, MIT |accessdate=10/01/2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101232305/http://web.mit.edu/catalog/front.degre.html |archive-date=2016-01-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2013-14年度，提供19類學士學位課程的工程學院最受歡迎，錄取了過半的學生，餘下的依次為：理學院、人文藝術與社會科學院、斯隆管理學院及建築學院。電子工程與-{zh:電腦;zh-cn:电子计算机;zh-hk:電腦; zh-tw:電腦}-科學為學生人數最多的課程<ref>{{cite web|title=Enrollment Statistics|url=http://web.mit.edu/registrar/stats/yrpts/index.html|publisher=MIT Office of the Registrar|accessdate=10/01/2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091007012833/http://web.mit.edu/registrar/stats/yrpts/index.html|archive-date=2009-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

所有大學生均需完成17個學院必修課程，它們被分為四大類：基礎科學、人際關係、文藝社科、體育運動<ref name="GIR">{{cite web|url=http://web.mit.edu/firstyear/2019/subjects/index.html|title=First-Year Academics: General Institute Requirements (GIRS)|publisher=Officer of the Registrar, MIT|date=2015|accessdate=10/03/2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003235119/http://web.mit.edu/firstyear/2019/subjects/index.html|archivedate=2015-10-03}}</ref>。新生之年的課程多半都是這些必修課程，它們亦為進入不同學系的條件之一，而無論學生升讀大二後的主修為何，都必須完成剩餘的必修課程。基礎科學包括了[[微積分|微積分]]（[[數學|數學]]）、[[物理學|物理學]]、[[化學|化學]]及[[生物學|生物學]]，前兩者為時兩個學期，其餘的僅佔一個學期。文藝社科必修課程修讀時間不得少於八學期。「人際關係」部分則要求學生分別在文藝社科及自己的主修課程中，選讀至少有兩個「以溝通為重」的課程。最後，所有學生還需接受[[游泳|游泳]]訓練，而非校隊成員亦須修畢為時一年的[[体育教育|體育]]班<ref name="GIR"/>。

一個課程通常包括了講堂、輔導課、每週功課及測試。雖然不少學生認為應付繁重的學業「猶如飲用消防栓噴出的水」<ref>{{cite book|title=Leadership and Organizational Culture: New Perspectives on Administrative Theory and Practice |editors=Thomas J. Sergiovanni, John Edward Corbally |chapter=Leadership as Reflection-in-Action |last=Schön |first=Donald A. |publisher=University of Illinois Press |year=1986 |isbn=0-252-01347-6 |url=http://books.google.com/?id=wfjpFezRhuYC&pg=PA59&lpg=PA59 |page=59 |quote=[In the sixties] Students spoke of their undergraduate experience as "drinking from a fire hose." |accessdate=2008-08-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Mattuck|first=Arthur|title=The Torch or the Firehose|year=2009|publisher=MIT OpenCourseWare|page=1|url=http://ocw.mit.edu/resources/res-18-004-the-torch-or-the-firehose-a-guide-to-section-teaching-spring-2009/online-publication/|access-date=2015-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150917053923/http://ocw.mit.edu/resources/res-18-004-the-torch-or-the-firehose-a-guide-to-section-teaching-spring-2009/online-publication/|archive-date=2015-09-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但麻省理工的大學生轉校率與全美其他研究型大學相若，並沒有特別高<ref name=":0">{{cite web |url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/rankings/national-universities/freshmen-least-most-likely-return |title=Average Freshmen Retention Rates: National Universities |publisher=U.S. News and World Report |accessdate=09/06/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110302212851/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/rankings/national-universities/freshmen-least-most-likely-return |archive-date=2011-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。每個秋季學期的課程不會對學生作出等級評核，而僅報告「通過與否」，這減少了學生的一些壓力。若學生未能通過，則其學期成績報告不會出現有關課程的名字。不過，春季學期的課堂則會對學生作出「A、B、C 等」的評級，未能通過者同樣不獲記錄在案<ref name="Freshman Year">{{cite web |url=http://catalog.mit.edu/mit/undergraduate-education/academic-programs/freshman-year/ |title=Undergraduate Education - Freshman Year |publisher=Officer of the Registrar, MIT |accessdate=10/03/2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929023549/http://catalog.mit.edu/mit/undergraduate-education/academic-programs/freshman-year/ |archive-date=2015-09-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1969年，瑪格麗特在麻省理工學院創立了大學生研究計劃，提供網站作平台，方便他們能直接與教職員或研究員接觸<ref>{{cite web|title=MIT UROP: Basic Information|url=http://web.mit.edu/UROP/basicinfo/index.html|publisher=MIT|accessdate=10/03/2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221081426/http://web.mit.edu/urop/basicinfo/index.html|archive-date=2015-12-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。多數的大學生均參與其中，以爭取學分或增廣見聞<ref>{{cite web |title=MIT Research and Teaching Firsts |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/special/firsts.html |accessdate=10/06/2006 |publisher=MIT News Office |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060915023328/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/special/firsts.html |archivedate=2006-09-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Undergraduate Research Opportunities Program|url=http://wiki.mitadmissions.org/UROP|publisher=MIT Admissions|accessdate=2012-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824175214/http://wiki.mitadmissions.org/UROP|archive-date=2012-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不少學生均表示此計劃有助他們[[科學期刊|發表論文]]、申請專利或[[創業公司|創業]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Use of Undergraduates in Research Is Hailed by M.I.T.; Inventions by Students |newspaper=[[紐約時報|''The New York Times'']] |last=Maeroff |first=Gene I. |date=01/11/1976}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://tech.mit.edu/V119/N47/UROP_turns_30.47f.html |title=An MIT Original, the Oft Replicated UROP Program Reaches 30 Years |last=Palmer |first=Matthew |date=10/05/1999 |newspaper=''The Tech'' |volume=119 |number=47 |access-date=2015-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516094138/http://tech.mit.edu/V119/N47/UROP_turns_30.47f.html |archive-date=2011-05-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

1970年，當時的學院關係部長本森河·斯奈德發表了《隱藏的課程設置》一書，批評麻省理工的教育使學生傾向於跟從一些不成文規定。那些懂得在教學系統中取巧而非具扎實根基的學生，反而能獲取較高的畢業成績。例如，一些學生團體中的高年級生會編制「課程秘笈」，記錄不同課程的每週功課及測試的答案，供師弟、師妹「參考」。在斯奈德眼中，這些小動作阻礙了個人的創意及知識發展<ref>{{cite book |last=Benson |first=Snyder |title=The Hidden Curriculum |year=1970 |publisher={{link-en|麻省理工出版社|MIT Press|MIT Press}} |isbn=0-262-69043-8 |url=https://mitpress.mit.edu/catalog/item/default.asp?tid=4398&ttype=2 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114174521/http://mitpress.mit.edu/catalog/item/default.asp?tid=4398&ttype=2 |archivedate=2012-11-14 |access-date=2015-10-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Mahoney|first=Matt|title=Unwritten Rules|url=http://www.technologyreview.com/mitnews/427509/unwritten-rules/|accessdate=2012-06-21|journal=[[麻省理工科技評論|''Technology Review'']]|date=2012}}</ref>。

<!--研究生教育-->
麻省理工學院的博士與碩士學位全面地涵蓋數理工、社會科學、人文等學術領域，也有一些為跨學科學位。研究生課程並非大類收生，申請者需直接與個別學系聯絡，而六所學院的收生標準、申請方法、錄取率等也各有不同。校方向部分獲錄取的博士生提供獎學金（逾三成）、教學助理（一成）及研究助理（近五成）的職位。不少研究生課程同時開放給合資格的大學生報讀<ref>{{cite web|title=Graduate Education|url=http://web.mit.edu/facts/graduate.html|work=MIT Facts 2015|publisher=MIT|accessdate=10/04/2015|date=2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018171036/http://web.mit.edu/facts/graduate.html|archive-date=2015-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===研究概況===
[[File:Kismet_robot_20051016.jpg|thumb]]。]]
麻省理工學院於1934年加入[[美國大學協會|美國大學協會]]，校內的研究活動頻繁，2014年的研究開支合共六億七千多萬美金<ref name=research_facts>{{cite web|title=RESEARCH EXPENDITURES|url=http://web.mit.edu/facts/research-expend.html|work=MIT Facts 2015|publisher=MIT|accessdate=10/04/2015|date=2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151220171344/http://web.mit.edu/facts/research-expend.html|archive-date=2015-12-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中，聯邦政府（[[美國衛生與公共服務部|衛生與公共服務部]]、[[美國國防部|國防部]]、[[美國能源部|能源部]]、[[國家科學基金會|國家科學基金會]]、[[美國太空總署|-{zh:太空總署;zh-cn:国家航空航天局;zh-hk:太空總署;zh-tw:國家航空暨太空總署;}-]]）向校方提供的資助金額最高<ref name=research_facts/>。除了教職員，校方還額外聘請了約1,300名研究人員<ref name=MITFac>{{cite web|last=Office of the Provost|title=MIT Faculty and Staff|url=http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/faculty_staff.html|publisher=MIT|accessdate=10/04/2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929005618/http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/faculty_staff.html|archive-date=2015-09-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這些工作人員在2011年公佈了632項發明創造，獲頒發153個專利，並分別賺得八千五百多萬及六千九百多萬美金的現金與特許權使用費收入<ref>{{cite web |title=TLO Statistics for Fiscal Year 2011 |url=http://web.mit.edu/tlo/www/about/office_statistics.html |publisher=MIT |accessdate=10/04/2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120521090351/http://web.mit.edu/tlo/www/about/office_statistics.html |archivedate=2012-05-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

在電子科技方面，麻省理工研究人員發明或大幅發展了[[磁芯記憶體|磁芯記憶體]]、[[雷達|雷達]]、{{link-en|庫侖阻力|Coulomb blockade}}與[[慣性導航系統|慣性導航系統]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ieee.org/about/ieee_history.html |title=IEEE History Center: MIT Radiation Laboratory |publisher=IEEE |accessdate=06/09/2008 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65CfhpwXB?url=http://www.ieee.org/about/ieee_history.html |archive-date=2012-02-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RLE History"/>。其中，{{link-en|哈羅德·金頓|Harold Eugene Edgerton}}為發展[[高速攝影|高速攝影]]及[[聲納|聲納]]技術的先驅<ref>{{cite web |url=http://edgerton-digital-collections.org/techniques/high-speed-photography |accessdate=2009-11-28 |title=High Speed Camera |author=Harold "Doc" Edgerton |date=2009-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100207035431/http://edgerton-digital-collections.org/techniques/high-speed-photography |archive-date=2010-02-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[克勞德·夏農|-{zh:克勞德·夏農;zh-hans:克劳德·香农; zh-hant:克勞德·夏農}-]]為現代[[信息論|信息論]]的發展貢獻良多，亦開拓了[[數碼電路|-{zh:數碼電路;zh-hans:数字电路; zh-hk:數碼電路; zh-tw:數位電路}-]]及[[邏輯代數|邏輯代數]]的應用<ref>{{cite news |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/shannon.html |title=MIT Professor Claude Shannon dies; was founder of digital communications |date=2001-02-27 |publisher=MIT News Office |accessdate=10/04/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121091241/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/shannon.html |archive-date=2012-01-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[電腦科學|-{zh:電腦;zh-cn:电子计算机;zh-hk:電腦; zh-tw:電腦}-科學]]方面，麻省理工教職員及研究人員[[諾伯特·維納|諾伯特·維納]]、[[馬文·閔斯基|馬文·閔斯基]]、[[約瑟夫·維森鮑姆|約瑟夫·維森鮑姆]]、{{link-en|帕特里克·溫斯頓|Patrick Winston}}、[[羅德尼·布魯克斯|羅德尼·布魯克斯]]、[[羅納德·李維斯特|羅納德·李維斯特]]，分別對控制論、人工智能、計算機語言、機器學習、機器人技術、加密技術的發展奠下了基礎<ref name="RLE History">{{cite web |url=http://www.rle.mit.edu/about/about_history.html |title=Research Laboratory of Electronics at MIT: History |publisher=MIT |accessdate=06/09/2008 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080515234702/http://www.rle.mit.edu/about/about_history.html |archivedate=2008-05-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Guttag |first=John |title=The Electron and the Bit, Electrical Engineering and Computer Science at MIT, 1902–2002 |year=2003}}</ref>。共有九位[[圖靈獎|圖靈獎]]及七位[[查爾斯·斯塔克·德雷珀獎|查爾斯·斯塔克·德雷珀獎]]得主曾經或現在於麻省理工學院學習或工作<ref name=TuringAward>{{cite web|last=Office of the Provost|title=A. M. Turing Award|url=http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/acm-turing.html|publisher=MIT|accessdate=2011-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101021055314/http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/acm-turing.html|archive-date=2010-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

除了應用科學，麻省理工的自然科學研究亦為蓬勃，共有[[各大學諾貝爾獎得主列表|近六十位諾貝爾物理學、化學、生理學或醫學獎]]、三位[[沃爾夫獎|沃爾夫獎]]得主與此校有所聯繫<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/dirac.html |title=Dirac Medal |publisher=Office of Institutional Research, MIT |accessdate=2008-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101023181154/http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/dirac.html |archive-date=2010-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[次原子粒子|次原子粒子]]與[[量子物理學|量子物理學]]、新[[化學合成|化學合成法]]、[[免疫學|免疫學]]、[[腫瘤學|腫瘤學]]、[[分子生物學|分子生物學]]為獲獎者所研究的領域<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wolffund.org.il/cat.asp?id=25&cat_title=PHYSICS |title=Prize in Physics |publisher=Wolf Foundation |accessdate=2010-10-04 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65DR3JlSI?url=http://www.wolffund.org.il/cat.asp?id=25 |archive-date=2012-02-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="IR Nobel">{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/nobel.html |title=Nobel Prize |publisher=Office of Institutional Research, MIT |accessdate=2008-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329175439/http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/nobel.html |archive-date=2010-03-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 麻省理工亦首次發現[[正子電子偶|正子電子偶]]、合成型[[盤尼西林|盤尼西林]]、[[肌萎縮性脊髓側索硬化症|肌萎縮性脊髓側索硬化症]]、[[亨丁頓舞蹈症|亨丁頓舞蹈症]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2002/deutsch.html |title=Martin Deutsch, MIT physicist who discovered positronium, dies at 85 |date=2002-08-20 |accessdate=06/12/2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010154309/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2002/deutsch.html |archive-date=2008-10-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Professor John C. Sheehan Dies at 76 |date=04/01/1992 |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1992/sheehan-0401.html |publisher=MIT News Office |accessdate=06/12/2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080630091223/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1992/sheehan-0401.html |archive-date=2008-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://w3.mit.edu/newsoffice/tt/1990/may09/23124.html |title=Self-Reproducing Molecules Reported by MIT Researchers |publisher=MIT News Office |date=05/09/1990 |accessdate=06/12/2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516120912/http://w3.mit.edu/newsoffice/tt/1990/may09/23124.html |archivedate=2008-05-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。學校的[[埃里克·蘭德|埃里克·蘭德]]教授為[[人類基因組計劃|人類基因組計劃]]的主力研究人員之一<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Lander |first=Eric |title=Initial sequencing and analysis of the human genome |publisher=Nature |year=2001 |doi=10.1038/35057062 |journal=Nature |volume=409 |pmid=11237011 |last2=Linton |first2=LM |last3=Birren |first3=B |last4=Nusbaum |first4=C |last5=Zody |first5=MC |last6=Baldwin |first6=J |last7=Devon |first7=K |last8=Dewar |first8=K |last9=Doyle |first9=M| displayauthors = 8 |issue=6822 |pages=860–921}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Eric S. Lander |url=http://www.broadinstitute.org/about/bios/bio-lander.html |publisher=Broad Institute |accessdate=06/09/2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090704234000/http://www.broadinstitute.org/about/bios/bio-lander.html |archive-date=2009-07-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MIT Firsts">{{cite web |title=MIT Research and Teaching Firsts |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/special/firsts.html |publisher=MIT |accessdate=06/12/2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080531233441/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/special/firsts.html |archivedate=2008-05-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[傑羅姆·萊特文|傑羅姆·萊特文]]教授亦改寫了認知科學的發展史<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1998/03/31/science/last-rites-for-a-plywood-palace-that-was-a-rock-of-science.html |title=Last Rites for a 'Plywood Palace' That Was a Rock of Science |last=Hilts |first=Philip J. |date=1998-03-31 |newspaper=''The New York Times'' |accessdate=10/04/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120421014446/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/03/31/science/last-rites-for-a-plywood-palace-that-was-a-rock-of-science.html |archive-date=2012-04-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

除了十多位諾貝爾經濟學獎得主之外，九位[[約翰·貝茨·克拉克獎|約翰·貝茨·克拉克獎]]亦為麻省理工的師生、校友<ref name="IR Nobel"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/clark.html |title=John Bates Clark Medal |publisher=Office of Institutional Research, MIT |accessdate=2008-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101023181144/http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/clark.html |archive-date=2010-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|莫里斯·哈勒|Morris Halle}}及[[諾姆·杭士基|-{zh-hans:诺姆·乔姆斯基; zh-hant:諾姆·杭士基}-]]合創了[[生成文法|生成文法]]與[[音位學|音位學]]文本<ref>{{cite news|title=A Changed Noam Chomsky Simplifies |last=Fox |first=Margalit|date=12/05/1998 |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D01EEDB113BF936A35751C1A96E958260 |work=The New York Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2001/jan/20/society.politics |title=Conscience of a nation |work=The Guardian |date=2001-01-20 |accessdate=08/12/2008 |last=Jaggi |first=Maya |location=London |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100114172108/http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2001/jan/20/society.politics |archive-date=2010-01-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。麻省理工的[[麻省理工媒體實驗室|媒體實驗室]]亦作出了包括[[建構主義_(學習理論)|建構主義]]在內的多個非傳統人文藝術或社會科學研究<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/2002/01/08/0108medialab.html |title=MIT Media Lab Tightens Its Belt |last=Herper |first=Matthew |date=01/08/2002 |accessdate=08/12/2008 |work=Forbes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101202163925/http://www.forbes.com/2002/01/08/0108medialab.html |archive-date=2010-12-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=M.I.T. Media Lab at 15: Big Ideas, Big Money |date=04/07/2009 |work=The New York Times |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2000/11/09/technology/09MITT.html |first=Lisa |last=Guernsey |access-date=2015-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100904061151/http://www.nytimes.com/2000/11/09/technology/09MITT.html |archive-date=2010-09-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

不過，學校也曾出現[[科學不端行為|科學不端行為]]的醜聞。諾貝爾獎得主[[戴維·巴爾的摩|戴維·巴爾的摩]]於1986年接受不端行為調查，更在1991年接受國會聆訊<ref name="Baltimore">{{cite news|title=Journal Cites New Evidence ex-MIT Scientist Faked Data |last=Saltus |first=Richard |work=The Boston Globe |date=1990-09-28}}</ref><ref name="Nobel Winner">{{cite news|title=Nobel Winner Is Caught Up in a Dispute Over Study |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=940DE7D8133FF931A25757C0A96E948260&scp=22&sq=Massachusetts+Institute+of+Technology+misconduct&st=nyt |work=The New York Times |date=04/12/1988 |last=Boffey |first=Philip}}</ref>。西奧多教授自2000年以來，曾多次批評麻省理工行政部門撇清林肯實驗室一次[[導彈防禦|導彈防禦]]測試的潛在不端行為<ref>{{cite news|title=MIT Faces Charges of Fraud, Cover-up on Missile Test Study |work=The Boston Globe |date=2002-11-29 |last=Abel |first=David}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Pierce |first=Charles P. |title=Going Postol |work=The Boston Globe |date=2005-10-23 |url=http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2005/10/23/going_postol/ |accessdate=2008-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080508003331/http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2005/10/23/going_postol/ |archive-date=2008-05-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。陸帆·巴瑞斯副教授於2005年因科學行為不端而被停職，[[美國研究操守調查部|美國研究操守調查部]]亦於2009年判其有罪<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ori.hhs.gov/misconduct/cases/VanParijs.shtml |title=Case Summary – Luk Van Parijs |publisher=Office of Research Integrity, U.S. Department of Health & Human Services |date=2009-01-23 |accessdate=12/02/2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611090045/http://ori.hhs.gov/misconduct/cases/VanParijs.shtml |archivedate=2009-06-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nature.com/news/2009/090203/full/news.2009.74.html |title=Former MIT biologist penalized for falsifying data |publisher=Nature News |date=02/03/2009 |first=Eugenie |last=Reich |access-date=2015-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016005821/http://www.nature.com/news/2009/090203/full/news.2009.74.html |archive-date=2015-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===學術聯盟===
麻省理工學院一直以來都和學界、工業界、政府等機構組成學術研究聯盟<ref>{{cite journal |title = A Survey of New England: A Concentration of Talent |journal=The Economist |date=1987-08-08 |quote=MIT for a long time... stood virtually alone as a university that embraced rather than shunned industry.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=MIT: Shaping the Future |first=Edward B. |last=Roberts |chapter=An Environment for Entrepreneurs |publisher=MIT Press |year=1991 |location=Cambridge, MA |isbn=0262631415 |quote=The war made necessary the formation of new working coalitions... between these technologists and government officials. These changes were especially noteworthy at MIT.}}</ref>。1946年，康普頓校長、喬治·多里奧特（[[哈佛商學院|哈佛商學院]]教授）及美林·格里斯德（-{zh:麻省; zh-cn:马萨诸塞州; zh-tw:麻薩諸塞州;zh-hk:麻省}-投資信託基金會主席）共同創立了全美第一間[[風險投資|風險投資]]公司——{{link-en|美國研究與發展集團|American Research and Development Corporation}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Shlaes |first=Amity |title=From the Ponderosa to the Googleplex: How Americans match money to ideas |work=State Department Press Release |publisher=U.S. Department of State |date=2008-05-14 |quote=Griswold, [MIT president] Compton, and various politicians handpicked Doriot to head American Research & Development, a new firm that would invest in [the] small, innovative companies that had been underserved by traditional capital markets.}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Simon |first=Jane |url=http://iipdigital.usembassy.gov/st/english/publication/2008/05/20080512161121jmnamdeirf0.424679.html |title=Route 128: How it developed, and why it's not likely to be duplicated |page=15 |work=New England Business |location=Boston |date=07/01/1985 |quote=Compton co-founded in 1946 what is believed to be the nation's first venture capital company.…  [He] and a group led by a Harvard professor [Doriot] founded one of the first venture capital companies, American Research & Development Corp. |access-date=2015-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713130047/http://iipdigital.usembassy.gov/st/english/publication/2008/05/20080512161121jmnamdeirf0.424679.html |archive-date=2015-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩年後，康普頓又成立了麻省理工工業聯絡計劃<ref>{{cite web |title=Industrial Liaison Program: About Us |publisher=MIT |year=2011 |url=http://ilp.mit.edu/about.jsp |quote=Established in 1948, the ILP continues … making industrial connections for MIT. |access-date=2015-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016005821/http://ilp.mit.edu/about.jsp |archive-date=2015-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1991年，麻省理工華盛頓辦公室面世，作為學校遊說政府給予更多的研究基金及協助制定科學政策的平台<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/dc/ |title=MIT Washington Office |accessdate=2007-03-18 |publisher=MIT Washington Office |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070207103414/http://web.mit.edu/dc/ |archivedate=2007-02-07 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=02/11/2001 |title=Hunt Intense for Federal Research Funds: Universities Station Lobbyists in Washington}}</ref>。麻省理工學院與鄰近的[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]一直存有合作及良性競爭關係。它們成立了[[哈佛-麻省理工醫療科技學院|哈佛-麻省理工醫療科技學院]]及{{link-en|博德研究中心|Broad Institute}}，兩校的學生亦可以報讀對方的課程而無需繳付額外的學費<ref name="EdPart">{{cite web|title=MIT Facts: Educational Partnerships|url=http://web.mit.edu/facts/partnerships.shtml|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104171108/http://web.mit.edu/facts/partnerships.html|archivedate=2009-01-04|accessdate=09/07/2010|year=2010|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此外两校也不乏合办项目，如與[[哈佛醫學院|哈佛醫學院]]合辦的{{link-en|醫學-哲學雙博士|MD-PhD}}學位<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hms.harvard.edu/md_phd/|title=The Harvard/MIT MD-PhD Program|accessdate=2019-03-23|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190312221613/http://www.hms.harvard.edu/MD%5FPhD/|archive-date=2019-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。麻省理工跨校課程夥伴還有[[衛斯理學院|-{zh-hans:衞斯理学院; zh-hant:衛斯理學院}-]]、[[波士頓大學|波士頓大學]]、[[布蘭迪斯大學|-{zh:布蘭迪斯大學;zh-hans:布兰迪斯大学; zh-hant:布蘭迪斯大學}-]]、[[塔夫茨大學|塔夫茨大學]]、{{link-en|麻省藝術與設計學院|Massachusetts College of Art and Design}}、{{link-en|波士頓美術博物館學院|School of the Museum of Fine Arts, Boston}}<ref name="EdPart"/>。2002年，校方與[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]成立了劍橋-麻省理工研究中心，兩校也舉辦了本科生交流計劃。此校與不少波士頓的獨立研究機構關係密不可分：{{link-en|查爾斯·斯塔克德雷珀實驗室|Charles Stark Draper Laboratory}}、{{link-en|白石研究中心|Whitehead Institute}}、[[伍茲霍爾海洋研究中心|伍茲霍爾海洋研究中心]]等，雙方有密切的交流<ref name="EdPart"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://web.mit.edu/progettorocca|title=Roberto Rocca Project|accessdate=2009-11-19|publisher=MIT|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091211214008/http://web.mit.edu/progettorocca/|archive-date=2009-12-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。麻省理工國際科技倡議計劃負責處理與其他國家之院校的教研合作<ref name="EdPart"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/misti/ |title=MIT International Science and Technology Initiatives |accessdate=2007-03-17 |publisher=MIT |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070210111938/http://web.mit.edu/misti/ |archivedate=2007-02-10 }}</ref>。

[[麻省理工科技評論|《麻省理工科技評論》]]為針對大眾市場的雜誌，由麻省理工學院透過一子公司出版，同時也是該校的校友雜誌<ref>{{cite web|title=About Us|url=http://www.technologyreview.com/about/|work=''Technology Review''|publisher=MIT|accessdate=06/05/2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Alumni Benefits|url=http://alum.mit.edu/benefits/AlumniBenefits|publisher=MIT Alumni Association|accessdate=06/05/2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531120902/http://alum.mit.edu/benefits/AlumniBenefits|archive-date=2012-05-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除此，{{link-en|麻省理工出版社|MIT Press}}也是世上主要的{{link-en|大學出版社|University Press}}之一，主力出版有關科技的書刊<ref>{{cite web |url=https://mitpress.mit.edu/mitpress/history/default.asp |title=History – The MIT Press |accessdate=2007-03-18 |publisher=MIT |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070415034220/http://mitpress.mit.edu/mitpress/history/default.asp |archive-date=2007-04-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

不過，麻省理工學院及其學術聯盟亦曾受到一些批評。上世紀八九十年代，不少美國政治家及企業領袖批評包括麻省理工在內的多所美國大學，指它們將由納稅人資助的研究與技術開發項目轉移至跨國企業（尤其是面向[[日本經濟|日本]]的公司），這在一定程度上導致了美國二十世紀九十年代初的經濟衰退<ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0CEEDB153FF93AA25751C1A966958260&scp=1&sq=M.I.T.+Deal+with+Japan+Stirs+Fear+on+Competition&st=nyt |title=MIT Deal with Japan Stirs Fear on Competition |last=Kolata |first=Gina |date=1990-12-19 |accessdate=06/09/2008 |work=The New York Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=MIT Criticized for Selling Research to Japanese Firms |work=The Washington Post |date=1989-06-14 |first=William |last=Booth}}</ref>。1989年，[[美國司法部|司法部]]對麻省理工、八間[[常春藤盟校|常春藤盟校]]及另外11所大學展開調查，並於1991年提出起訴，指有關院校涉嫌在年度交流大會上，有意進行{{link-en|價格操縱|Price fixing}}（該會旨在避免院校間的學生資助或獎學金競價戰）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950DE2DC1E3CF933A2575BC0A96F948260 |title=Price-Fixing Inquiry at 20 Elite Colleges |work=The New York Times |date=08/10/1989 |accessdate=2008-12-16 | first=David | last=Johnston}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D0CE2DB173DF930A25750C0A967958260 |title=23 College Won't Pool Discal Data |last=Chira |first=Susan |date=1991-03-13 |accessdate=2008-12-16 |work=The New York Times}}</ref>。常春藤盟校答應[[庭外和解|庭外和解]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D0CE3D81E38F930A15756C0A967958260 |title=Ivy Universities Deny Price-Fixing But Agree to Avoid It in the Future |work=The New York Times |last=DePalma |first=Anthony |date=1991-05-23 |accessdate=2008-12-16}}</ref>，但麻省理工卻否認這觸犯了反競爭法<ref name="Overlap">{{cite news|title=MIT Ruled Guilty in Anti-Trust Case |work=The New York Times |date=09/02/1992 |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CE1DC1439F930A3575AC0A964958260 |last=DePalma |first=Anthony |accessdate=2008-07-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CE0DE1E38F935A15755C0A964958260 |title= Price-Fixing or Charity? Trial of M.I.T. Begins |last=DePalma |first=Anthony |date=1992-06-26 |accessdate=2008-08-13 |work=The New York Times}}</ref>。校方認為大會只是為了確保資助金能顧及更多有需要的學生。司法部最終於1994年撤銷了控訴<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1994/settlement-0105.html |title=Settlement allows cooperation on awarding financial-aid |publisher=MIT Tech Talk |year=1994 |accessdate=2007-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080630091228/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1994/settlement-0105.html |archive-date=2008-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CE5DC113BF932A15751C1A965958260 |title=MIT Suit Over Aid May Be Settled |first=William |last=Honan |date=1993-12-21 |accessdate=2008-07-16 |work=''The New York Times''}}</ref>。

===校內館藏===
麻省理工學院圖書館系統由多所涵蓋不同學科的圖書館組成，主要包括了巴克（工程）、杜威（經濟）、海登（文理）、路易斯（音樂）及羅奇（藝術建築）圖書館。館藏囊括二百九十萬冊印刷本、二百四十萬份縮微本、四萬九千個印刷或電子文獻、六百七十個參考數據庫。過去十年裡，館方較為著重電子書籍的重要性<ref>{{cite web|last=Geraci|first=Diane|title=Information Resources|url=http://web.mit.edu/annualreports/pres10/2010.13.00.pdf|work=MIT Reports to the President 2009–2010|publisher=MIT Reference Publications Office|accessdate=2012-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109083513/http://web.mit.edu/annualreports/pres10/2010.13.00.pdf|archive-date=2012-11-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。館內重要收藏包括路易斯音樂圖書館內的二十及二十一世紀音樂檔，利斯視覺藝術中心內的當代藝術展品，以及康普頓畫廊的跨學科展覽品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/music/contents.html |title=Lewis Music Library |publisher=MIT |accessdate=2010-10-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100707163440/https://libraries.mit.edu/music/contents.html |archivedate=2010-07-07 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://listart.mit.edu/about |title=MIT List Visual Arts Center |publisher=MIT |accessdate=10/01/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101010033652/http://listart.mit.edu/about |archive-date=2010-10-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/museum/exhibitions/compton.html |title=Compton Gallery |publisher=MIT Museum |accessdate=10/01/2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100806185321/http://web.mit.edu/museum/exhibitions/compton.html |archivedate=2010-08-06 }}</ref>。校方會定期撥出款項，以建立或翻新其戶外或可供公眾參觀的雕塑作品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mit.edu/~lvac/percent/index.html |title=MIT Percent-for-Art Program |publisher=MIT |accessdate=10/01/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511183718/http://www.mit.edu/~lvac/percent/index.html |archive-date=2011-05-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://listart.mit.edu:8080/Prt2*1$15*1943 |title=MIT Public Art Collection |publisher=MIT |accessdate=10/01/2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090718110730/http://listart.mit.edu:8080/Prt2*1$15*1943 |archivedate=2009-07-18 }}</ref>。

麻省理工博物館成立於1971年，主要收藏與學校歷史文化有關的文藝、紀念品。校方積極參與公眾藝術推廣活動，包括每年一次的劍橋科學節<ref name="MITMuseum">{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/museum/about/mission.html |title=MIT Museum: Mission and History |publisher=MIT |accessdate=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130502022529/http://web.mit.edu/museum/about/mission.html |archive-date=2013-05-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===大學排名===
{{美國大學排名
<!-- 國內名次 -->
| ARWU_NU       = 3
