麻省理工學院在多個排行榜上均名列前茅，並以理工見長<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Avery |first1=Christopher |last2=Glickman |first2=Mark E. |last3=Hoxby |first3=Caroline M |last4=Metrick |first4=Andrew |title=A Revealed Preference Ranking of U.S. Colleges and Universities, NBER Working Paper No. W10803 |date=2005 |publisher=National Bureau of Economic Research |url=http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=601105 |journal= |author= |access-date=2015-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017145723/http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=601105 |archive-date=2015-10-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此校的工程學院在1995年[[美國國家科學研究委員會|國家科研會]]報告中位列榜首<ref name="1995 NRC">{{cite web|url=http://www.stat.tamu.edu/~jnewton/nrc_rankings/nrc1.html|title=NRC Rankings|accessdate=10/09/2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080926121702/http://www.stat.tamu.edu/~jnewton/nrc_rankings/nrc1.html|archive-date=2008-09-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了工程，[[電腦科學|-{zh:電腦;zh-cn:电子计算机;zh-hk:電腦; zh-tw:電腦}-科學]]、[[數學|數學]]、[[自然科學|自然科學]]、[[商業學|商業學]]、[[語言學|語言學]]也是學校的強項<ref name="encyclopedia1"/>。1999至2009年期間，麻省理工（根據[[路透社|路透社]]的調查）的全球論文引用率為第十七<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sciencewatch.com/inter/ins/09/09Top20Overall/|title=The Most-Cited Institutions Overall, 1999–2009|publisher=Sciencewatch|accessdate=2015-10-19|date=2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091005083214/http://sciencewatch.com/inter/ins/09/09Top20Overall/|archive-date=2009-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[泰晤士高等教育|泰晤士高等教育]]》增刊的《全球大學就業排名》（2014年）顯示，麻省理工畢業生的就業率位列全球第六、全美第四<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/news/global-employability-university-ranking-2014-results/2017406.article|title=Global Employability University Ranking 2014 top 100|publisher=''Times Higher Education''|date=2014|accessdate=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810113421/https://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/news/global-employability-university-ranking-2014-results/2017406.article|archive-date=2015-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>；《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》2011年的調查則指，此校畢業生的平均工資金額排名全球第七、全美第六<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/imagepages/2011/10/20/education/20iht-SReducEmploy20-graphic.html?ref=education|title=What Business Leaders Say|publisher=''The New York Times''|date=2011|accessdate=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101203554/http://www.nytimes.com/imagepages/2011/10/20/education/20iht-SReducEmploy20-graphic.html?ref=education|archive-date=2015-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==學校生活==
===學生群體===
{| style="text-align:center; float:left; font-size:85%; margin-right:2em;" class="wikitable"
|+ 麻省理工學生人口統計（2017年）<ref name=Diversity>{{cite web|url=http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/students/diversity.html|title=Student Body Diversity|work=MIT Office of the Provost|date=2014|accessdate=2015-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025045014/http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/students/diversity.html|archive-date=2015-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
