2014-15年度，麻省理工學院共有11,319名學生，以研究生居多，[[男女同校|男女比例相若]]<ref name="Enrollment Statistics"/>。於1870年入學的[[艾倫·愛華露·理查茲|艾倫·愛華露·理查茲]]為此校的第一名女性學生，亦是第一位女性教職員（她留校任教[[環境化學|環境化學]]）<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.chemheritage.org/discover/chemistry-in-history/themes/public-and-environmental-health/public-health-and-safety/richards-e.aspx |author= Chemical Heritage Foundation |title= Ellen Swallow Richards |year= 2005 |work= Chemical Achievers, The Human Face of Chemical Sciences |accessdate= 11/04/2006 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20101206184112/http://www.chemheritage.org/discover/chemistry-in-history/themes/public-and-environmental-health/public-health-and-safety/richards-e.aspx |archive-date= 2010-12-06 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。學校女學生的比例自1993年有顯著的上升，從原本的三成多些，但現在近一半。校方所錄取的國際生來自115個海外地區<ref>{{Cite book |last = Simha |first = O. R. |title = MIT campus planning 1960–2000: An annotated chronology |year = 2003 |pages = 32–33 |url = https://books.google.com/?id=ldq-ZgxszzMC&lpg=PA32&pg=PA32| isbn = 978-0-262-69294-6 |quote=In 1959, 158 women were enrolled at MIT. |publisher = ''MIT Press''}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |last = Stratton |first = J. A. |title = The president's report 1960 |year = 1960 |page = 49 |url = http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/presidents-reports/1960.pdf |quote = Registration: In 1959–60 ... [o]ne hundred and fifty-five women were enrolled, [2.5 percent of student body].... |access-date = 2015-10-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304121656/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/mithistory/presidents-reports/1960.pdf |archive-date = 2016-03-04 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://groups.csail.mit.edu/mac/users/hal/women-enrollment-comm/final-report-ch1.html |title= Chapter 1: Male/Female enrollment patterns in EECS at MIT and other schools |date= 01/03/1995 |accessdate= 12/08/2006 |author= EECS Women Undergraduate Enrollment Committee |work= Women Undergraduate Enrollment in Electrical Engineering and Computer Science at MIT |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100731091513/http://groups.csail.mit.edu/mac/users/hal/women-enrollment-comm/final-report-ch1.html |archive-date= 2010-07-31 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

上世紀末至本世紀初，一連串的學生死亡事件使麻省理工受到各大媒體的注意，該校的學生文化尤其成為焦點<ref>{{cite news |last=Healy |first=Patrick |title=11 years, 11 suicides – Critics Say Spate of MIT Jumping Deaths Show a 'Contagion' |work=The Boston Globe |date=02/05/2001 |pages=A1}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Massachusetts Institute of Technology Looks for Ways to Deal with the Incidence of Student Suicides in Recent Years |publisher=National Public Radio |date=2001-08-29 |last=Smith |first=Tovia}}</ref>。1997年，一年級生斯科特·克魯格在其中一個兄弟會的會所內酒精中毒身亡，學校自此便要求所有新生入住校內宿舍<ref name="Krueger">{{cite news |url=http://chronicle.com/article/MIT-s-Inaction-Blamed-for/14196 |title=MIT's Inaction Blamed for Contributing to Death of a Freshman |work=The Chronicle of Higher Education |date=10/06/1998 |accessdate=10/07/2006 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515031437/http://chronicle.com/article/MIT-s-Inaction-Blamed-for/14196 |archive-date=2011-05-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Institute Will Pay Kruegers $6M for Role in Death |url=http://tech.mit.edu/V120/N42/42krueger.42n.html |accessdate=10/04/2006 |date=2000-09-15 |last=Levine |first=Dana |newspaper=The Tech |volume=120 |number=42 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104152301/http://tech.mit.edu/V120/N42/42krueger.42n.html |archive-date=2009-01-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2000年，學生伊麗莎白·申自殺，引起社會爭議<ref name="Shin">{{cite news |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F00EED7113FF93BA15757C0A9649C8B63&sec=health&pagewanted=4 |work=The New York Times |title=Who Was Responsible for Elizabeth Shin? |date=2002-04-28 |accessdate=10/07/2006 |first=Deborah |last=Sontag |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080604003737/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F00EED7113FF93BA15757C0A9649C8B63 |archive-date=2008-06-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.psychiatrictimes.com/display/article/10168/54106 |title= Suicide Prevention on Campus |author= Elizabeth Fried Ellen, LICSW |publisher= Psychiatric Times |year= 2002 |accessdate= 2006-06-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080507182711/http://www.psychiatrictimes.com/display/article/10168/54106 |archive-date= 2008-05-07 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。有指此校自殺率偏高，校方未有照顧到學生的[[精神健康|精神健康]]。2001年底，學校推出一系列的學生精神健康服務，包括了增加教職員人數及精神醫療中心的服務時間，效果不俗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/mhtf-facts.html |publisher=MIT New Office |title=MIT Mental Health Task Force Fact Sheet |date=2001-11-14 |accessdate=2006-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080630091259/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/mhtf-facts.html |archive-date=2008-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/12/03/education/03suicide.html?pagewanted=print&position= |title=Worried Colleges Step Up Efforts Over Suicide |work=The New York Times |date=12/03/2004 |accessdate=01/06/2009 |last=Arenson |first=Karen |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115025606/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/12/03/education/03suicide.html?pagewanted=print&position= |archive-date=2012-11-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/mhtf-1128.html |publisher= MIT News Office |title= Clay endorses Mental Health Task Force Recommendations |date= 2001-11-28 |accessdate= 2006-06-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080630091253/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/mhtf-1128.html |archive-date= 2008-06-30 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

===傳統文化===
麻省理工學院的師生信奉[[精英政治|唯才主義]]，並非常重視技術能力<ref>{{cite web |url= http://web.mit.edu/admissions/pdf/MITinstructions.pdf |format= PDF |title= MIT freshman application & financial aid information |first= Marilee |last= Jones |accessdate= 01/02/2007 |publisher= MIT Admissions Office |quote= We are a meritocracy. We judge each other by our ideas, our creativity and our accomplishments, not by who our families are. |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20061107035149/http://web.mit.edu/admissions/pdf/MITinstructions.pdf |archivedate= 2006-11-07 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.federalreserve.gov/boardDocs/speeches/2006/20060609/default.htm |title=2006 Commencement Speech at MIT |first=Ben S. |last=Bernanke |date=06/09/2006 |accessdate=01/02/2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061007204443/http://www.federalreserve.gov/boarddocs/speeches/2006/20060609/default.htm |archivedate=2006-10-07 }}</ref>。校方從沒有頒授[[榮譽學位|榮譽學位]]、體育獎學金、[[拉丁文學位榮譽|拉丁文學位榮譽]]或禮儀學位<ref>{{cite web |url = http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/commdegrees.html |title = No honorary degrees is an MIT tradition going back to... Thomas Jefferson |publisher = MIT News Office |date = 06/08/2001 |accessdate = 05/07/2006 |quote = MIT's founder, William Barton Rogers, regarded the practice of giving honorary degrees as 'literary almsgiving ...of spurious merit and noisy popularity...' |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060414025857/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2001/commdegrees.html |archive-date = 2006-04-14 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，除了[[溫斯頓·丘吉爾|溫斯頓·丘吉爾]]（1949年）及[[薩爾曼·魯西迪|薩爾曼·魯西迪]]（1993年）曾獲得榮譽教授的職銜<ref>{{cite news |first=Daniel C. |last=Stevenson |url=http://tech.mit.edu/V113/N61/rushdie.61n.html |title=Rushdie Stuns Audience 26–100 |volume=113 |number=61 |newspaper=The Tech |access-date=2015-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100725052034/http://tech.mit.edu/V113/N61/rushdie.61n.html |archive-date=2010-07-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

不少高年級生均配戴又大又重的畢業紀念戒指<ref name="Brass Rat">{{cite book|title=Massachusetts Curiosities: Quirky Characters, Roadside Oddities, & Other Offbeat Stuff |publisher=Globe Pequot |year=2004 |isbn=0-7627-3070-6 |last=Gellerman |first=Bruce |author2=Erik Sherman |pages=65–66}}</ref><ref name=BrassRat2013>{{cite news|last=Pourian|first=Jessica J.|title=2013's Brass Rat unveiled|url=http://tech.mit.edu/V131/N5/ringpremiere.html|accessdate=06/12/2011|newspaper=The Tech|volume=131|number=5|date=2011-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026153320/http://tech.mit.edu/V131/N5/ringpremiere.html|archive-date=2011-10-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此戒指始創於1929年，官方名稱為「標準科技戒」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://alumweb.mit.edu/classes/1993/brassrat.html |title=Ring History ('93 class webpage) |accessdate=2006-12-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061214164648/http://alumweb.mit.edu/classes/1993/brassrat.html |archivedate=2006-12-14 }}</ref>。本科與研究生都有自己的版本，每年的式樣並不相同，但均為三片式設計：一面顯示麻省理工印章，另外兩面則分別刻有畢業年份及河狸的模樣<ref name="Brass Rat"/>。除此，戒指時常被學生印上「{{lang|en|IHTFP}}」五個字母，此乃「我討厭這該死的地方」一句的[[首字母縮寫|英文縮寫]]（此句常在學生之間流行），但亦被包裝為「我找到了真正的的天堂」、「學院裡的教授是最好的」等句的縮寫<ref>{{cite web |last=Bauer |first=M.J. |title=IHTFP |url=http://www.mit.edu/people/mjbauer/ihtfp.html |accessdate=2005-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100621134258/http://www.mit.edu/people/mjbauer/ihtfp.html |archive-date=2010-06-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===團體活動===
[[File:Huntbeginsinlobby7.jpg|thumb]]
麻省理工有逾380個學生活動團體，包括了校園廣播站、《理工報》（校報）編輯團隊、創業比賽舉辦單位<ref>{{cite web |title=MIT Association of Student Activities |url=http://web.mit.edu/asa/resources/group-list.html |accessdate=11/01/82006 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328001556/http://web.mit.edu/asa/resources/group-list.html |archive-date=2010-03-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。非傳統的學會包括了[[鐵路模型技術俱樂部|鐵路模型技術俱樂部]]、民間舞蹈團。校內師生亦經常透過學校的博物館舉辦公眾推廣活動<ref>{{cite web |title=MIT Outreach Database |url=http://mitpsc.mit.edu/outreach/home/search |accessdate=09/07/2010 |publisher=MIT |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511132424/http://mitpsc.mit.edu/outreach/home/search |archive-date=2011-05-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。每年的一月為「自由活動學期」，有上百個課堂、講堂、示範教學課程、團體活動供學生選擇，其中，「解謎行動」最為受歡迎<ref name="Globe">{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2005/01/23/her_mystery_achievement_to_boldly_scavenge_at_mit/ |last=Bridges |first=Mary |work=The Boston Globe |title=Her Mystery achievement: to boldly scavenge at MIT |date=2005-01-23 |accessdate=2007-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060310085154/http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2005/01/23/her_mystery_achievement_to_boldly_scavenge_at_mit/ |archive-date=2006-03-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。每年約有250名學生利用這段時間進入各個公司實習<ref>{{Cite news |last=Kirkpatrick |first=J. |year=2011 |title=Students head off to varied externships |newspaper=The Tech |volume=131 |issue=59 |url=http://tech.mit.edu/V131/N59/externship.html |access-date=2015-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016005821/http://tech.mit.edu/V131/N59/externship.html |archive-date=2015-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Kirkpatrick |first=J. |year=2011 |title=Record 294 participate in MIT Externship Program |newspaper=The Tech |volume=131 |issue=57 |url=http://tech.mit.edu/V131/N57/externship.html |access-date=2015-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016202823/http://tech.mit.edu/V131/N57/externship.html |archive-date=2015-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

不少學生喜歡加入「黑客」行列，探索校園各個區域及進行惡作劇<ref>{{cite book |last=Peterson |first=T.F. |title=Nightwork: A History of Hacks and Pranks at MIT |url=https://archive.org/details/nightworkhistory0000pete |publisher=MIT Press|isbn=978-0-262-66137-9 |year=2003}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=These Are Not Your Ordinary College Pranks |work=The Boston Globe |date=04/01/2003 |last=Biskup |first=Agnieska}}</ref>。這也是[[加州-麻省理工學院競爭|此校與加州理工學院的競爭模式]]。

===體育競賽===
麻省理工共有31支校隊，涵蓋不同體育範疇，是[[國家大學體育協會|國家大學體育協會]]丙組中，最為全面的校隊之一。{{link-en|新英格蘭男女體育聯盟|New England Women's and Men's Athletic Conference}}、{{link-en|新英格蘭足球聯盟|New England Football Conference}}、{{link-en|朝聖者袋棍球聯賽|Pilgrim Lacrosse League}}<br>甲組：{{link-en|東部大學划船聯會|Eastern Association of Rowing Colleges}}均為其參與的跨校體育競賽項目<ref>{{cite web |author=Kathryn Krtnick, Asst. Dir. of Communications |title=Re: NCAA Media Inquiry |publisher=Natl. Collegiate Athletic Assn |date=2012-11-28 |url=http://mitcrimeclub.org/ncaa121128.pdf |quote=List of institutions that sponsor the most sports: Bowdoin College and Williams College – 32; MIT – 31. |access-date=2015-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514130055/http://mitcrimeclub.org/ncaa121128.pdf |archive-date=2013-05-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Athletics">{{cite web |author=Dept. of Athletics |title=2012–13 Quick Facts |publisher=MIT |date=2012 |url=http://mit.edu/athletics/www/department/DAPERQuickFacts09.pdf |quote=Intercollegiate Athletics: 33 varsity sports. |access-date=2015-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130219210811/http://mit.edu/athletics/www/department/DAPERQuickFacts09.pdf |archive-date=2013-02-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年的預算削減導致八個校隊項目被逼取消<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/sports/colleges/articles/2009/04/24/mit_forced_to_cut_8_varsity_sports/ |title=MIT forced to cut 8 varsity sports |date=2009-04-24 |first=John |last=Powers |work=The Boston Globe |access-date=2015-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430132159/http://www.boston.com/sports/colleges/articles/2009/04/24/mit_forced_to_cut_8_varsity_sports/ |archive-date=2009-04-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===住宿安排===
[[File:Simmons_Hall,_MIT,_Cambridge,_Massachusetts.JPG|thumb]]
所有的麻省理工本科生均可在未來四年裡，入住12所本科宿舍中的其中一所<ref>{{cite web |url=http://housing.mit.edu/undergraduate/residences |title=Undergraduate Residence Halls |author=MIT Housing Office |accessdate=10/01/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100621093628/http://housing.mit.edu/undergraduate/residences |archive-date=2010-06-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在校居住的學生可得到駐校研究生導師、輔導員或教職員的協助<ref>{{cite web |title=Residential Life Live-in Staff |url=http://web.mit.edu/reslife/rlp/ra-grt.html |publisher=MIT |accessdate=06/01/2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320123544/http://web.mit.edu/reslife/rlp/ra-grt.html |archivedate=2012-03-20 }}</ref>。由於學生可以選擇自己心儀的宿舍，人以群分，各宿舍都有着自己的特色。其中，由《耶魯日報》工作人員編寫的《2010年本科大學指南》中提到<ref>{{cite book|title=The Insider's Guide to the Colleges, 2010 |url=https://archive.org/details/insidersguidetoc00yale_5 |author=Yale Daily News Staff |year=2009 |publisher=St. Martin's Griffin |isbn=0-312-57029-5 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/insidersguidetoc00yale_5/page/377 377]–380}}</ref>：「麻省理工東西校園的分隔是該校的特色之一。東校園有着強烈的[[反文化|反文化]]色彩。」

麻省理工學生亦積極加入希臘文合作社住房制度，校內共有36個[[兄弟會與姊妹會|兄弟會與姊妹會]]及一些獨立社團<ref>{{cite web |title=MIT Facts: Housing |year=2010 |url=http://web.mit.edu/facts/housing.html |accessdate=10/01/2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914193127/http://web.mit.edu/facts/housing.html |archive-date=2008-09-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013-14學年，共有近九成的本科生選擇住校，近一半加入了兄弟會，逾三成加入了姊妹會<ref name="Enrollment Statistics"/>。兄弟會多集中在西校園，那些獨立社團因學校的歷史背景而多在[[後灣|後灣]]區<ref>{{cite web |title=Undergraduate and Graduate Residence Halls, Fraternities, Sororities, and Independent Living Groups @ MIT |url=http://web.mit.edu/reslife/fsilg/map.pdf |publisher=MIT Residential Life |accessdate=06/01/2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120508222758/http://web.mit.edu/reslife/fsilg/map.pdf |archivedate=2012-05-08 }}</ref>。

學校為單身研究生提供五所宿舍，有兩間公寓讓已婚學生的家人入住<ref>{{cite web |title=Graduate residences for singles & families |url=http://housing.mit.edu/graduatefamily/residences |accessdate=10/01/2010 |author=MIT Housing Office |publisher=MIT |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100620170109/http://housing.mit.edu/graduatefamily/residences |archivedate=2010-06-20 }}</ref>。

==著名人物==
===教職員===
[[File:Ford-MIT_Nobel_Laureate_Lecture_Series_2000-09-18.jpg|thumb]]、[[保羅·森穆遜|-{zh:保羅·森穆遜;zh-hans:保罗·萨缪尔森;zh-hk:保羅·森穆遜;zh-tw:保羅·薩繆爾森}-]]、[[羅拔·索洛|-{zh:羅拔·索洛;zh-tw:勞勃·梭羅;zh-cn:罗伯特·索洛;zh-hk:羅拔·索洛}-]]。]]
{{Asof|2014}}，麻省理工學院共有1,021位教職員，女性佔了224名<ref name=MITFactFacStaff/>。教職員負責講堂、給予本科及研究生指導、出席學術委員會，以及進行研究。有[[各大學諾貝爾獎得主列表|逾三十名]]麻省理工的教職員為[[諾貝爾獎|諾貝爾獲獎者]]，以[[諾貝爾物理學獎|物理學]]及[[諾貝爾經濟學獎|經濟學]]獎居多<ref name="Faculty Awards">{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/nobel.html |title=Awards and Honors |publisher=Institutional Research, Office of the Provost |accessdate=11/01/2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329175439/http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/nobel.html |archive-date=2010-03-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除此，[[國家科學獎章|國家科學獎章]]、{{link-en|國家技術與創新獎章 (美國)|National Medal of Technology and Innovation|國家技術與創新獎章}}、[[古根海姆獎學金|古根海姆獎學金]]、[[傅爾布萊特計畫|-{zh-hans:福布莱特; zh-hant:傅爾布萊特}-學者]]、[[麥克阿瑟獎|麥克阿瑟獎]]均為此校教職員所獲得的殊榮<ref name="MITFactFacStaff" />。那些對學校及有關學術領域作出巨大貢獻的教職員會獲任命「學院教授」一職，他們的自由度會更大，有較多特權，亦只需向教務長負責。

不少麻省理工教職員同時獲選為政府部門的領袖。前教授[[玛西娅·麦克纳特|玛西娅·麦克纳特]]在職期間為[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]]局長<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usgs.gov/aboutusgs/organized/bios/mcnutt.asp|title=Marcia McNutt, Director, U.S. Geological Survey|publisher=U.S. Department of the Interior, U.S. Geological Survey|accessdate=2015-05-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723005513/http://www.usgs.gov/aboutusgs/organized/bios/mcnutt.asp|archivedate=2015-07-23}}</ref>，城市研究學教授{{link-en|澤維爾·布里格斯|Xavier Briggs}}為[[美國行政管理與預算局|美國行政管理與預算局]]副局長<ref>{{cite news |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2009/briggs-0120.html |title=DUSP's Briggs joins Obama administration |publisher=MIT News Office |date=2009-01-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330050839/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2009/briggs-0120.html |archivedate=2014-03-30 |accessdate=2015-11-01 }}</ref>，生物學教授[[埃里克·蘭德|埃里克·蘭德]]為{{link-en|美國總統科技顧問委員會|United States President's Council of Advisors on Science and Technology}}聯合主席<ref>{{cite news |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2008/lander-pcast-1222.html |title=Lander named to Obama's science team |date=2008-12-22 |publisher=MIT News Office |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330060448/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2008/lander-pcast-1222.html |archivedate=2014-03-30 |accessdate=2015-11-01 }}</ref>，而教職員[[歐內斯特·莫尼茲|歐內斯特·莫尼茲]]亦於2013年獲委任為[[美國能源部長|美國能源部長]]<ref name=nytimes-nominee>{{cite news|last1=Calmes|first1=Jackie|last2=Broder|first2=John|title=Obama Announces 3 Cabinet Nominations|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/03/05/us/politics/obama-to-nominate-new-heads-for-energy-department-and-epa.html?pagewanted=1&_r=0&hp|accessdate=03/04/2013|newspaper=The New York Times|date=03/04/2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510042847/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/03/05/us/politics/obama-to-nominate-new-heads-for-energy-department-and-epa.html?pagewanted=1&_r=0&hp|archive-date=2013-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url =http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-02-06/news/sns-rt-us-usa-cabinet-energybre91602h-20130206_1_energy-secretary-energy-department-ernest-moniz | title =Exclusive: Obama considering MIT physicist Moniz for energy secretary - sources | publisher =chicagotribune.com | author =Roberta Rampton | date =02/06/2013 | accessdate =2013-02-24 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130510122405/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-02-06/news/sns-rt-us-usa-cabinet-energybre91602h-20130206_1_energy-secretary-energy-department-ernest-moniz | archive-date =2013-05-10 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

此校曾被指對教職員存有歧視。於1984年被解僱的科技史學家{{link-en|大衛·F·奴布|David F. Noble}}成為新聞焦點。他曾多次批評麻省理工學院及其他一些研究型大學過於依賴商業及軍事機構的贊助，故外界擔心學校是否有足夠的[[學術自由|學術]]與[[言論自由|言論自由]]<ref name="Noble">{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9A0DE7DF1130F933A2575AC0A960948260&n=Top%2fReference%2fTimes%20Topics%2fOrganizations%2fM%2fMassachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology
| title = Professor Sues M.I.T. Over Refusal of Tenure |work=The New York Times |date=09/10/1986 |accessdate=10/03/2006}}</ref>。前物料科學教授格雷琴於1994年控告麻省理工，指校方拒絕她的終身教職申請是出於性別歧視。多年後，有關控訴以沒有公開的賠償金額得到解決<ref name="Male Domain"/><ref name="Kalonji">{{cite news|title=Ex-MIT professor who was denied tenure files sex bias suit |work=The Boston Globe |last=Vaznis |first=James |date=1994-01-15}}</ref>。1997年，-{zh:麻省; zh-cn:马萨诸塞州; zh-tw:麻薩諸塞州;zh-hk:麻省}-反歧視委員會發表了一份報告，支持[[麻省大學|波士頓麻省大學]]教授詹姆斯·詹寧斯對麻省理工學院的指責。他指麻省理工城市研究與規劃學系的一名高級教職委員對他存有種族歧視，沒有受理他的教職申請<ref name="Jennings">{{cite news|title=MCAD supports scholar's claim of bias by MIT; University Offered job, but no tenure |date=1997-10-22 |work=The Boston Globe |last=Dowdy |first=Zachary}}</ref>。2006-07年，此校拒絕給予非裔美國人幹細胞學教授詹姆斯終身教職位，引發極大爭議以及[[絕食|絕食]]行動<ref name="Sherley">{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/news/local/articles/2007/02/06/professor_accuses_mit_of_racism/ |title=Professor accuses MIT of racism |work=The Boston Globe |accessdate=2007-12-18 |date=02/06/2007 |first=April |last=Simpson |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100910004417/http://www.boston.com/news/local/articles/2007/02/06/professor_accuses_mit_of_racism/ |archive-date=2010-09-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。弗蘭克·L.·道格拉斯教授辭職以示不滿<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/news/local/articles/2007/06/04/mit_center_director_resigns_in_protest_of_tenure_decision/ |title=MIT center director resigns in protest of tenure decision |work=The Boston Globe |accessdate=2007-12-19 |date=06/04/2007 |first=Peter |last=Schworm |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100910001938/http://www.boston.com/news/local/articles/2007/06/04/mit_center_director_resigns_in_protest_of_tenure_decision/ |archive-date=2010-09-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但詹姆斯21位同事發表聯合聲明，指他們相信這位教授沒遭不公平對待<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/news/local/articles/2007/02/06/professor_accuses_mit_of_racism/|title=Professor accuses MIT of racism|author=April Simpson|work=Globe Staff|date=02/06/2007|access-date=2015-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100910004417/http://www.boston.com/news/local/articles/2007/02/06/professor_accuses_mit_of_racism/|archive-date=2010-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1998年的一份校內報告指，理學院與工程學院對女教職員存有性別歧視<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/fnl/women/women.html |title=A Study on the Status of Women Faculty in Science at MIT |publisher=MIT Faculty News Letter |year=1999 |access-date=2015-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413084419/http://web.mit.edu/fnl/women/women.html |archive-date=2010-04-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，雖說有關調查方式備受爭議<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uaf.edu/northern/mitstudy/ |first=Judith |last=Kleinfeld |title=MIT Tarnishes Its Reputation with Gender Junk Science |accessdate=04/10/2007 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070208134206/http://www.uaf.edu/northern/mitstudy/ |archivedate=2007-02-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://old.nationalreview.com/nr_comment/nr_comment041001b.shtml |title=Feminist Mythology |first=Kathryn Jean |last=Lopez |date=04/10/2001 |publisher=National Review |accessdate=04/10/2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100521093527/http://old.nationalreview.com/nr_comment/nr_comment041001b.shtml |archivedate=2010-05-21 }}</ref>。自此以後，這兩所學院均曾讓女職員擔任院長一職，而學校也曾由多位女校長帶領<ref name="Male Domain">{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/news/education/higher/articles/2007/12/06/tenure_at_mit_still_largely_a_male_domain/ |title=Tenure at MIT Still Largely a Male Domain |last=Wertheimer |first=Linda |work=The Boston Globe |date=12/06/2007 |accessdate=2008-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511182549/http://www.boston.com/news/education/higher/articles/2007/12/06/tenure_at_mit_still_largely_a_male_domain/ |archive-date=2008-05-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[神經科學|神經生物學家]][[蘇珊·霍克菲爾德|蘇珊·霍克菲爾德]]便是該校第一位女校長<ref name="Hockfield">{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/hockfield/biography.html |title=Susan Hockfield, President, Massachusetts Institute of Technology – Biography |publisher=MIT |accessdate=2008-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419140329/http://web.mit.edu/hockfield/biography.html |archive-date=2010-04-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===校友===
[[File:Buzz_Aldrin_(S69-31743).jpg|thumb]]太空員[[巴茲·艾德靈|巴茲·艾德靈]]。]]
[[File:Kofi_Annan.jpg|thumb]][[科菲·安南|科菲·安南]]。]]
{{Asof|2014}}，共有[[各大學諾貝爾獎得主列表|逾30位諾貝爾獲獎者]]、47位[[羅德獎學金|羅德學者]]、61位[[馬歇爾獎學金|馬歇爾獎學金得主]]為麻省理工學院的校友<ref name=IRAwardsHonors>{{cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/index.html |title=Awards and Honors |author=MIT Office of Institutional Research |accessdate=03/11/2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100422234222/http://web.mit.edu/ir/pop/awards/index.html |archive-date=2010-04-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

著名政界人物包括：{{link-en|美聯儲主席|Chair of the Federal Reserve}}[[本·伯南克|本·伯南克]]、{{link-en|麻省第一國會選區|Massachusetts's 1st congressional district|-{zh:麻省; zh-cn:马萨诸塞州; zh-tw:麻薩諸塞州;zh-hk:麻省}-第一國會選區}}代表[[約翰·奧利弗|約翰·奧利弗]]、{{link-en|加州第十三國會選區|Massachusetts's 1st congressional district}}代表{{link-en|彼得·斯塔克|Pete Stark}}、{{link-en|美國國家經濟委員會|United States National Economic Council|國家經濟委員會}}主席[[勞倫斯·薩默斯|勞倫斯·薩默斯]]、前[[美國總統經濟顧問委員會|經濟顧問委員會]]主席{{link-en|克里斯蒂娜·羅默|Christina Romer}}、伊朗外交部長[[阿里·阿克巴爾·薩利希|阿里·阿克巴爾·薩利希]]、[[以色列總理|以色列總理]][[班傑明·納坦尼雅胡|-{zh-hans:本雅明·内塔尼亚胡;zh-hant:班傑明·納坦尼雅胡}-]]、[[歐洲中央銀行行長|歐洲中央銀行行長]][[馬里奧·德拉吉|馬里奧·德拉吉]]、[[印度儲備銀行|印度儲備銀行]][[拉古拉姆·拉詹|拉古拉姆·拉詹]]、[[外交及聯邦事務大臣|外交及聯邦事務大臣]][[文禮彬|-{zh:文禮彬;zh-hans:戴维·米利班德;zh-hk:文禮彬;zh-tw:大衛·米勒班}-]]、[[希臘總理|希臘總理]][[盧卡斯·帕帕季莫斯|盧卡斯·帕帕季莫斯]]、前[[聯合國秘書長|聯合國秘書長]][[科菲·安南|科菲·安南]]、伊拉克部長理事會主席[[艾哈邁德·沙拉比|艾哈邁德·沙拉比]]。

麻省理工一眾校友亦創辦了不少著名公司：[[英特爾|英特爾]]（[[羅伯特·諾伊斯|羅伯特·諾伊斯]]）、[[麥克唐納飛行器公司|麥克唐納飛行器公司]]（[[詹姆斯·史密斯·麥克唐納|詹姆斯·史密斯·麥克唐納]]）、[[道格拉斯飛行器公司|道格拉斯飛行器公司]]（[[老唐納德·威爾士·道格拉斯|老唐納德·威爾士·道格拉斯]]）、[[3Com|3Com]]（[[羅伯特·梅特卡夫|羅伯特·梅特卡夫]]）、[[德州仪器|德州仪器]]（{{link-en|塞西爾·霍華德·格林|Cecil Howard Green}}）、[[高通公司|高通公司]]（[[安德魯·維特比|安德魯·維特比]]）、[[博士音響|博士音響]]（{{link-en|阿馬爾·百色|Amar Bose}}）、[[科氏工業集團|科氏工業集團]]（{{link-en|弗雷德·C·科赫|Fred C. Koch}}）、[[洛克威爾|-{zh:洛克威爾;zh-hant:洛克威爾;zh-hans:罗克韦尔;}-]]（威拉德·羅克韋爾）、[[基因泰克|基因泰克]]（{{link-en|羅伯特·A·斯旺森|Robert A. Swanson}}）、[[Dropbox|Dropbox]]（[[德魯·休斯頓|德魯·休斯頓]]）及[[金寶湯公司|金寶湯公司]]（{{link-en|約翰·湯普森·多蘭斯|John Thompson Dorrance}}）。[[衛報|《衛報》]]指：「一項調查顯示麻省理工校友創辦了25,800間公司，僱用了三百萬人。這些公司每年利潤總值1.9兆[[美金|美金]]，若麻省理工是一個國家的話，那麼它會是全球第十一大經濟體。」<ref name="Entrepreneur">{{cite journal|url=http://www.entrepreneur.com/article/217327|title=Gurus and Grads|journal=Entrepreneur|date=2010-09-20|author1=Ericka Chickowski|author=|access-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026122334/https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/217327|archive-date=2015-10-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kauffman">{{cite news |title=Kauffman Foundation study finds MIT alumni companies generate billions for regional economies |publisher=MIT News Office |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2009/kauffman-study-0217.html |date=2009-02-17 |accessdate=11/05/2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328013404/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2009/kauffman-study-0217.html |archive-date=2010-03-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=The MIT factor: celebrating 150 years of maverick genius |author=Ed Pilkington |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/2011/may/18/mit-massachusetts-150-years-genius |newspaper=''The Guardian'' |date=2011-05-18 |accessdate=11/05/2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707190748/http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/2011/may/18/mit-massachusetts-150-years-genius |archive-date=2013-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

逾三分一的美國載人航天飛行計劃的[[太空人|太空人]]曾於麻省理工接受教育（包括[[太陽神11號|-{zh-hans:阿波羅11号; zh-tw:阿波羅11號; zh-hk:太陽神11號}-]][[太陽神登月艇|登月艇]]機師[[巴茲·艾德靈|巴茲·艾德靈]]），人數為各大高校（除[[美國聯邦軍事院校|美國聯邦軍事院校]]外）之最<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mitadmissions.org/topics/pulse/notable_alumni/ |title=Notable Alumni |accessdate=11/04/2006 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061127113157/http://www.mitadmissions.org/topics/pulse/notable_alumni/ |archivedate=2006-11-27 }}</ref>。校友兼前教職員[[錢學森|錢學森]]為[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]火箭科技發展的先驅。

其他範疇的著名人物包括了作家[[休·洛夫廷|休·洛夫廷]]、雕塑家丹尼爾·切斯特、{{link-en|波士頓樂隊|Boston (band)}}的吉他手{{link-en|湯姆·肖爾茨|Tom Scholz}}、[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]及[[獨立電視新聞|獨立電視新聞]]政治顧問大衛·沃爾特、[[紐約時報|《紐約時報》]]專欄作家兼[[諾貝爾經濟學獎|諾貝爾經濟學獎]]得主[[保羅·克魯明|-{zh:保羅·克魯明; zh-hans:保罗·克鲁格曼; zh-hk:保羅·克魯明; zh-tw:保羅·克魯曼}-]]、[[鐘形曲線：美國社會中的智力與階層結構|《鐘形曲線：美國社會中的智力與階層結構》]]作者查爾斯·默里、美國最高法院大樓建築師{{link-en|卡斯·吉爾伯特|Cass Gilbert}}、[[普立茲克獎|-{zh:普立茲克獎;zh-hans:普利兹克奖; zh-hant:普立茲克獎}-得主]]建築師[[貝聿銘|貝聿銘]]與[[戈登邦·沙夫特|戈登邦·沙夫特]]<ref>{{cite book|title=Children's Books and Their Creators|first=Anita |last=Silvey|isbn=0-395-65380-0|year=1995|publisher=Houghton Mifflin |page=415 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=DzV5M07MZigC&pg=RA4-PA415}}</ref><ref name="WDL">{{cite web|url = http://www.wdl.org/en/item/11376/|title = Study for Woolworth Building, New York|website = World Digital Library|date = 12/10/1910|accessdate = 2013-07-25|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6IPLeIzqP?url=http://www.wdl.org/en/item/11376/|archive-date = 2013-07-26|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

